0members%20and%20contributors%20of%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERead%20the%20full%20statement%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%2C%20the%20undersigned%2C%20are%20deeply%20shocked%20and%20concerned%20about%20the%20arrest%20of%20two%20persons%20including%20the%20NewsClick%20editor%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20under%20various%20sections%20of%20the%20draconian%20UAPA%20and%20the%20blanket%20raids%20in%20the%20houses%20of%20about%2046%20newspersons%20associated%20with%20the%20NewsClick%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20October%203rd.%20This%20includes%20Githa%20Hariharan%2C%20Urmilesh%2C%20Aunindyo%20Chakravarti%2C%20Sohail%20Hashmi%2C%20Teesta%20Setalvad%2C%20Sanjay%20Rajoura%2C%20Paranjoy%20Guha%20Thakurta%20and%20Anuradha%20Raman.%20All%20of%20them%20are%20well-known%20journalists%20and%20activists%20who%20have%20a%20commendable%20body%20of%20work%20to%20their%20credit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20against%20NewsClick%20is%20a%20chilling%20attempt%20to%20silence%20their%20brave%20voices.%20Criticism%20is%20essential%20for%20a%20democracy%20and%20any%20attempt%20to%20mute%20voices%20is%20an%20assault%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20spirit.%20By%20foisting%20cases%20under%20sections%20of%20UAPA%20and%20sealing%20the%20office%20of%20NewsClick%20the%20State%20is%20attempting%20to%20vilify%20journalists%20who%20have%20consistently%20and%20fearlessly%20spoken%20truth%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20also%20come%20to%20know%20that%20many%20of%20them%20were%20detained%20by%20the%20Delhi%20police%2C%20and%20several%20of%20them%20have%20had%20their%20phones%20and%20laptops%20confiscated.%20This%20does%20not%20merely%20constitute%20a%20violation%20of%20their%20privacy%20but%20is%20also%20illegal%20since%20the%20devices%20have%20been%20confiscated%20without%20court%20orders%20and%20without%20their%20owners%20being%20informed%20of%20the%20details%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20record%20with%20concern%20that%20there%20have%20been%20reports%20in%20the%20past%20of%20manufactured%20%E2%80%98pieces%20of%20evidence%E2%80%99%20being%20planted%20in%20the%20confiscated%20devices%20of%20activists%20who%20were%20detained%20under%20UAPA.%20We%20are%20genuinely%20worried%20that%20similar%20attempts%20will%20be%20made%20in%20the%20case%20of%20journalists%20of%20NewsClick.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20urge%20stakeholders%20and%20concerned%20citizens%20to%20speak%20up%20against%20this%20harassment%20of%20NewsClick%20and%20its%20contributors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20dark%20moment%2C%20we%20record%20our%20deep%20appreciation%20of%20NewsClick%E2%80%99s%20stellar%20work%20in%20journalism%20and%20stand%20firmly%20in%20solidarity%20with%20all%20its%20staff%20and%20contributors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESignatories%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAruna%20Roy%3Cbr%3E%20Geetanjali%20Shree%3Cbr%3E%20K.R.%20Meera%3Cbr%3E%20P.%20Sainath%3Cbr%3E%20Perumal%20Murugan%3Cbr%3E%20Ramachandra%20Guha%3Cbr%3E%20T.M.%20Krishna%3Cbr%3E%20V.%20Geetha%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696503627000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05153723%2Fnewsclick-statement.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fstate-vilifying-journalists-who-speak-truth-to-power-renowned-writers-activists-on-newsclick-case%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20action%20against%20NewsClick%20is%20a%20chilling%20attempt%20to%20silence%20their%20brave%20voices.%20Criticism%20is%20essential%20for%20a%20democracy%20and%20any%20attempt%20to%20mute%20voices%20is%20an%20assault%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20spirit.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fstate-vilifying-journalists-who-speak-truth-to-power-renowned-writers-activists-on-newsclick-case%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20on%20ambassador's%20'alert'%20about%20fallo