on%20should%20be%20upheld%20if%20poverty%20has%20to%20be%20eradicated%2C%20and%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20specific%20mechanisms%20to%20support%20women%20and%20transgender%20communities%20within%20the%20discriminated%20and%20vulnerable%20population.%20She%20was%20speaking%20during%20the%20second%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%20(SDG)%20Summit%20that%20was%20held%20in%20New%20York%20last%20month%20to%20review%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%202030%20Agenda%20for%20Sustainable%20Development%20and%20the%2017%20SDGs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20a%20person%20belonging%20to%20the%20Dalit%20community%2C%20representing%20the%20stakeholder%20group%20on%20communities%20discriminated%20on%20work%20and%20dissent%2C%20including%20Dalits%2C%20Haratin%2C%20Roma%2C%20Killambola%2C%20and%20other%20people%20who%20are%20socially%20and%20economically%20excluded%20and%20discriminated%20intergenerationally.%20We%20number%20around%20270%20million%20across%20all%20continents%20together%20with%20the%20indigenous%20people%2C%20Afro-descendant%20people%2C%20people%20with%20disability%2C%20LGBTQIA%2B.%20Within%20these%20marginalised%20communities%20we%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20actually%20are%20the%20%E2%80%98leave%20no%20one%20behind%E2%80%99%20that%20the%20SDGs%20are%20currently%20focusing%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%9CLeave%20No%20One%20Behind%E2%80%9D%20is%20a%20pledge%20of%20the%202030%20SDG%20that%20was%20adopted%20by%20members%20of%20the%20UN%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20there%20is%20a%20need%20to%20overhaul%20the%20financial%20architecture%2C%20Beena%20put%20forth%20a%20multi-layered%20approach%20with%20which%20it%20should%20be%20done.%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20we%20need%20to%20take%20into%20consideration%20the%20debt%20trap%20the%20southern%20nations%20are%20facing.%20This%20is%20a%20crime%20and%20we%20cannot%20allow%20a%20huge%20proportion%20of%20our%20budgets%20in%20many%20countries%20over%2050%25%20to%20be%20spent%20on%20debt%20servicing.%20This%20must%20be%20dealt%20with%20ruthlessly%20to%20ensure%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20massive%20debt%20relief%20strategy.%20There%E2%80%99s%20another%20layer%20which%20we%20normally%20ignore%20within%20the%20SDG%20mechanism%2C%20the%20intra-national%20fiscal%20infrastructure%20in%20both%20the%20northern%20and%20southern%20countries%20which%20are%20excluding%20socially%20marginalised%20from%20accessing%20the%20financial%20resources%20of%20the%20national%20budgets%20and%20wealth.%20This%20is%20equally%20critical.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20suggested%20six%20things%20that%20can%20be%20followed%20by%20the%20UN%20to%20achieve%20the%20SDG%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCommunity%20engagement%3A%20involve%20the%20rights%20holder%20communities%20and%20decision-making%20processes%20regarding%20the%20allocation%20of%20funds%20and%20investments%20to%20ensure%20their%20needs%20and%20priorities%20are%20addressed%3B%20Targeted%20Budgeting%3A%20set%20portion%20of%20the%20nations%E2%80%99%20budget%20should%20be%20set%20aside%20to%20specially%20make%20them%20available%20to%20micro%20development%20of%20individuals%2C%20families%20and%20habitations%20where%20the%20socially%20excluded%20communities%20live.%20Some%20countries%20like%20India%2C%20Brazil%20and%20Mexico%20have%20adopted%20some%20of%20these%20significant%20steps%3B%20Socially%20responsible%20investment%20funds%3A%20promote%20the%20creation%20and%20growth%20of%20SRI%20%5BSocially%20Responsible%20Investment%5D%20funds%3B%20Inclusive%20financial%20services%3A%20local%20and%20community-based%20financing%2C%20international%20support%20engage%20with%20international%20organisations%20and%20donor%20agencies%20and%20development%20banks%20to%20mobilise%20financial%20resources%3B%20Engendering%20financial%20inclusion%3A%20we%20must%20also%20have%20specific%20mechanism%20to%20deal%20and%20to%20help%20support%20women%20and%20trans%20communities%20within%20these%20discriminated%20and%20vulnerable%20population.