%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20overall%20sentiment%20is%20that%20yes%2C%20Republicans%20and%20all%20Americans%20believe%20a%20hard%20day's%20work%20should%20mean%20you%20get%20a%20fair%20day's%20wage%2C%26quot%3B%20Alice%20Stewart%2C%20a%20veteran%20Republican%20strategist%20for%20several%20presidential%20campaigns%20and%20a%20CNN%20political%20commentator%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20we%20can%20do%20to%20help%20create%20jobs%20and%20create%20better-paying%20jobs%2C%20the%20better%20it%20is%20for%20the%20economy%20of%20this%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20conservatives%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emay%20prefer%20that%20advancement%20is%20done%20through%20the%20free%20market%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20many%20people%20are%20seeing%20a%20benefit%20in%20what%20unions%20have%20been%20able%20to%20do%20to%20create%20better%20jobs%20and%20better-paying%20jobs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Drake%20%E2%80%94%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20transportation%2C%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20supply-chain%20policy%20at%20the%20right-leaning%20US%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20%E2%80%94%20told%20Insider%20%26quot%3Bevery%20American%20can%20relate%20to%20getting%20a%2040%25%20pay%20increase%26quot%3B%20or%20wanting%20to%20increase%20their%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20these%20are%20universal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20these%20are%20things%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20folks%20can%20identify%20with.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUAW%20President%20Shawn%20Fain%20is%20rallying%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehis%20members%20with%20a%20broader%20message%20around%20the%20labor%20movement%20writ%20large%2C%20pitting%20the%20middle%20class%20against%20the%20%26quot%3Bbillionaire%20class.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20going%20to%20wreck%20the%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Fain%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Detroit%20at%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20strike%20earlier%20th