0have%20ever%20entered%20the%20workforce.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrake%20of%20the%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%2C%20however%2C%20said%20the%20way%20this%20was%20playing%20out%20might%20make%20businesses%20more%20reluctant%20to%20entertain%20having%20any%20sort%20of%20union%20representation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reality%20of%20this%20is%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20businesses%20are%20looking%20at%20these%20negotiations%20going%20forward%2C%20and%20I%20think%20they're%20appalled%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20UAW%20has%20to%20be%20really%20careful%20because%20they%20may%20win%20the%20battle%20but%20lose%20the%20overall%20war%20because%20a%20lot%20of%20companies%20are%20going%20to%20look%20at%20unions%20and%20think%20to%20themselves%2C%20'I%20don't%20want%20that%20happening%20to%20me.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20the%20UAW%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20prove%20following%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fformer-uaw-president-pleads-guilty-to-embezzlement-charges-11591213966%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyearslong%20federal%20criminal%20investigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20sent%20several%20prominent%20UAW%20leaders%20to%20prison.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20union%20is%20looking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuaw-auto-union-strike-could-change-industry-forever-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclaw%20back%20its%20influence%3C%2Fa%3E%20not%20just%20in%20the%20automotive%20industry%20but%20also%20as%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20labor%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarolyn%20Nippa%2C%20a%2026-year%20GM%20employee%20who%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuaw-strike-history-what-happened-during-2019-gm-union-stoppage-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewent%20on%20strike%20in%202019%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20plant%20closures%2C%20said%20she%20felt%20more%20energized%20by%20the%20union's%20demands%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20our%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Nippa%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWe%20did%20our%20part%20to%20try%20to%20help%20the%20company%20%E2%80%94%20we%20saved%20the%20company%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we're%20just%20asking%20back%20what%20we%20gave%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20adjusted%20for%20inflation%2C%20the%20average%20automotive-manufacturing%20wage%20has%20fallen%20some%20%2410%20an%20hour%20from%20its%20peak%20of%20about%20%2442%20an%20hour%20in%202003%2C%20according%20to%20data%20compiled%20for%20Insider%20by%20Jason%20Miller%2C%20a%20Michigan%20State%20University%20professor%20of%20supply-chain%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20happens%20as%20the%20burgeoning%20electric-vehicle%20sector%20creates%20organizing%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20the%20extent%20that%20the%20UAW%20is%20able%20to%20win%20a%20strong%20contract%2C%20that%20works%20as%20a%20message%20to%20nonunion%20workers%20about%20the%20advantages%20of%20organizing%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrias%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFain%20appears%20to%20recognize%20this%20opportunity%2C%20using%20his%20platform%20to%20speak%20often%20with%20people%20outside%20the%20UAW%20who%20support%20its%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStriking%20for%20a%20better%20future%20to%20protect%20our%20communities%20and%20to%20defeat%20corporate%20greed%20is%20not%20just%20our%20right.%20It's%20our%20duty%2C%26quot%3B%20Fain%20said%20on%20a%20Friday%20livestream%20with%20more%20than%2060%2C000%20viewers.%20%26quot%3BWe%20invite%20you%20to%20stand%20with%20us%20on%20the%20picket%20line%20if%20you%20support%20our%20cause.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuaw-strike-support-union-bipartisan-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696500121000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651d6c5a617692f0d03eb59b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22