ording%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D1b8da88fa1f27709175a9ee1a7548fc4d1816f2cb7aad4df8fd5dcb3b8d731b9%26postID%3D651b0cf9e40dc22aa93d1344%26postSlug%3Dai-content-editing-new-freelance-side-hustle-emerges-2023-10%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Ffiverr.com%252Fcp%252Fbusiness-trends-index-october-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enew%20report%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20the%20online-freelance%20platform%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-money-on-fiverr-freelance-writer-writing-jobs-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFiverr%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20highlighted%20the%20digital%20services%20that%20have%20recently%20surged%20in%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20six%20months%2C%20Fiverr%20searches%20by%20businesses%20and%20individuals%20for%20freelancers%20with%20AI-content-editing%20skills%20increased%20by%20over%2010%2C000%25%20worldwide%20compared%20to%20the%20prior%20six-month%20period%2C%20including%20growth%20of%20over%207%2C000%25%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Fiverr%20representative%20told%20Insider%20that%20pay%20for%20these%20projects%20varies%2C%20but%20typically%20starts%20at%20about%20%24100%20to%20%24125.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20AI-content%20editing%2C%20many%20of%20these%20searches%20came%20from%20businesses%20looking%20to%20%26quot%3Blegitimize%20AI-generated%20content%26quot%3B%20created%20with%20tools%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20representative%20said.%20Customers%20might%20ask%20freelancers%20to%20fine-tune%20AI-generated%20marketing%20materials%20or%20to%20optimize%20AI%20content%20for%20search%20engines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20many%20busy%20small-business%20owners%20and%20entrepreneurs%20who%20use%20AI%20to%20generate%20content%2C%20there%20is%20a%20worry%20that%20their%20content%20will%20get%20penalized%20by%20search%20engines%20or%20that%20their%20pieces%20won't%20read%20well%20to%20their%20target%20audience%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20representative%20said.%20%26quot%3BAI-content-editing%20services%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20always%20a%20human%20touch%20and%20that%20nothing%20is%20lost%20in%20translation%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI-generated%20content.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20representative%20also%20cited%20editing%20AI-generated%20slide%20decks%20used%20in%20business%20presentations%20as%20another%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20the%20proliferation%20of%20AI%2C%20you%20needed%20a%20person%20to%20write%20the%20text%2C%20build%20the%20graphics%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20representative%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20one%20Fiverr%20freelancer%20told%20us%2C%20now%20with%20AI%2C%20entire%20presentations%20can%20be%20built%20off%20of%20one%20headline.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EChatGPT's%20flaws%20could%20lead%20the%20demand%20for%20AI-editing%20skills%20to%20grow%20further%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBusinesses%20could%20be%20turning%20to%20AI-generated%20content%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons.%20In%20August%2C%20Time%20Magazine%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F6302710%2Fnao-medical-google-ai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20New%20York%20City-based%20urgent-care%20clinic%20Nao%20Medical%2C%20likely%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20boost%20its%20placement%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarketing-industry-using-ai-save-time-money-boost-productivity-study-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternet-search%20results%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20had%20flooded%20its%20website%20with%20articles%20such%20as%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20Are%20Unicorns%20Healthier%20Than%20Dragons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20more%20students%20and%20businesses%20dabble%20with%20generative%20AI%2C%20demand%20for%20content-editing%20services%20could%20continue%20to%20grow.%20Despite%20ChatGPT's%20impressive%20capabilities%2C%20it's%20been%20known%20to%2C%20at%20some%20times%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-openai-ceo-worst-case-ai-lights-out-for-all-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprovide%20misinformation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20even%20when%20it%20does%20get%20the%20facts%20right%2C%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgannett-pauses-ai-written-articles-after-social-media-mockery-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20always%20the%20best%20writer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20there's%20a%20potential%20downside%20to%20the%20growth%20of%20these%20AI%20opportunities%20for%20some%20freelancers%2C%20Sheraz%20Shoukat%2C%20an%20Australia-based%20Fiverr%20freelancer%20who%20offers%20a%20variety%20of%20writing%20services%2C%20including%20AI-content-editing%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20hasn't%20done%20much%20AI%20editing%20work%20so%20far%20and%20believes%20the%20widespread%20adoption%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-write-cover-letter-chatgpt-template-prompts-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etechnology%20like%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20lead%20to%20less%20demand%20for%20freelance%20writing%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20way%20more%20negative%20impact%20on%20our%20earnings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContent%20editing%20isn't%20the%20only%20AI%20skill%20that's%20seen%20a%20spike%20in%20interest%20on%20Fiverr.%20Over%20the%20last%20six%20months%2C%20searches%20for%20%26quot%3Bprompt%20engineering%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAI%20video%26quot%3B%20grew%20by%20over%207%2C000%25%20and%203%2C000%25%20worldwide%2C%20respectively.%20The%20starting%20pay%20for%20these%20gigs%20can%20be%20much%20higher%20than%20AI-content%20editing%20%E2%80%94%20up%20to%20%245%2C000%20per%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20freelancer%20who's%20getting%20paid%20to%20do%20work%20related%20to%20generative%20AI%20and%20willing%20to%20share%20your%20story%3F%20If%20so%2C%20reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ejzinkula%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-content-editing-new-freelance-side-hustle-emerges-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696500001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65170add3fb8f400198ad734%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-content-editing-new-freelance-side-hustle-emerges-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fiverr%20freelancers%20can%20earn%20over%20%24100%20per%20project%20to%20edit%20AI-generated%20content.%20Demand%20has%20grown%20by%20more%20than%2010%2C000%25%20over%20the%20the%20past%20six%20months.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzinkula%40insider.com%20(Jacob%20Zinkula)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-content-editing-new-freelance-side-hustle-emerges-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Bait%20And%20Switch%20-%20BJP's%20Charade%20Of%20Women's%20Quota%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20said%20that%20in%20politics%2C%20timing%20is%20everything.%20The%20re-introduction%20of%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20government%2C%20after%20almost%20a%20decade%20in%20office%2C%20right%20before%20the%20upcoming%20general%20election%2C%20is%20no%20exception.%20The%20timing%20of%20the%20move%20and%20the%20convoluted%20steps%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20attached%20to%20its%20execution%20has%20exposed%20the%20party's%20strategy%20for%20what%20it%20is%20-%20a%20shallow%20political%20charade.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImplementation%20Loopholes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArticle%20334A%2C%20which%20has%20been%20inserted%20in%20the%20Constitution%20to%20provide%20for%20women's%20reservation%2C%20says%20quota%20for%20women%20will%20take%20effect%20after%20a%20delimitation%20or%20redrawing%20of%20constituencies%20based%20on%20the%20first%20census%20after%20the%20law%20is%20enacted.%20Now%2C%20there%20is%20no%20credible%20reason%20to%20tie%20the%20reservation%20to%20the%20census%20or%20delimitation%2C%20and%20previous%20bills%20did%20not%20include%20a%20delimitation%20rider.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20the%20timeline%20for%20women's%20reservation%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20smokescreen.%20Without%20a%20miracle%2C%20women's%20reservation%20by%202029%20is%20a%20long%20shot.%20If%20the%20Census%20starts%20by%20February%202025%2C%20the%20delimitation%20will%20still%20have%20to%20be%20based%20on%20the%20Census%20after%202026%20because%20Article%2082%20directs%20a%20freeze%20on%20delimitation%20until%20the%20first%20Census%20after%202026.%20This%20means%20data%20from%20the%202031%20census%20might%20be%20the%20earliest%20reference.%20Considering%20the%20time%20taken%20by%20the%20Delimitation%20Commission%20in%20the%20past%2C%20and%20electoral%20roll%20revisions%20before%20the%20next%20elections%2C%20a%20more%20realistic%20cut-off%20might%20be%202039%2C%20unless%20circumstances%20change%20drastically.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20Modi%20government's%20past%20record%2C%20postponing%20something%20is%20akin%20to%20suggesting%20it%20might%20never%20happen.%20The%20postponement%20of%20women's%20reservation%20by%20the%20government%20casts%20serious%20doubts%20about%20its%20commitment%2C%20and%20renders%20this%20'reform'%20as%20the%20latest%20in%20the%20long%20list%20of%20BJP's%20'jumlas'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20Talk%2C%20No%20Action%3A%20Modi's%20Mirage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20PM%20Modi-led%20BJP%20government%20portrays%20itself%20as%20a%20champion%20of%20woman%20empowerment%2C%20the%20hypocrisy%20is%20becoming%20clearer%20by%20the%20day.%20The%20fact%20that%20BJP%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%2C%20accused%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20by%20woman%20wrestlers%2C%20was%20sitting%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20when%20the%20Bill%20was%20taken%20up%2C%20speaks%20for%20itself.%20He%20has%20been%20neither%20expelled%20by%20the%20party%20nor%20removed%20from%20his%20position.%20The%20BJP's%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20silence%20and%20the%20tactical%20whataboutery%20on%20violence%20against%20women%20in%20Manipur%20also%20displays%20a%20shocking%20lack%20of%20seriousness%20of%20the%20party%20in%20women-centric%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20Association%20of%20Democratic%20Reforms%20report%20suggests%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20MPs%20with%20cases%20of%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%20murder%2C%20and%20attempt%20to%20murder.%20The%20BJP%20has%20vociferously%2C%20and%20at%20times%20tacitly%2C%20stood%20by%20those%20who%20use%20abusive%20language%20and%20are%20involved%20in%20harassment%20and%20sexual%20offenses%20against%20women%2C%20and%20has%20encouraged%20leaders%20such%20as%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20and%20Kuldeep%20Sengar.%20The%20party's%20backing%20for%20perpetrators%20of%20heinous%20sexual%20crimes%20is%20glaring%20from%20the%20case%20of%202002%20Gujarat%20riots%20survivor%20Bilkis%20Bano.%20The%20BJP's%20policy%20and%20practice%20has%20normalised%20misogynistic%20behavior%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20the%20actions%20of%20its%20leaders%20and%20supporters%20are%20woefully%20unaddressed.%20The%20discrimination%20against%20and%20ill-treatment%20of%20women%20in%20India%20attracts%20stoic%20silence%20from%20the%20BJP's%20woman%20leaders%20such%20as%20Smriti%20Irani%20and%20Meenakshi%20Lekhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMissing%20OBC%20Quota%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20absence%20of%20an%20OBC%20quota%20in%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20has%20thrown%20a%20spotlight%20on%20the%20BJP's%20superficial%20commitment%20to%20affirmative%20action%20and%20genuine%20representation.%20The%20need%20for%20affirmative%20action%20in%20India%20to%20address%20the%20historical%20injustices%20has%20been%20invariably%20recognised.%20Political%20representation%20is%20one%20of%20the%20key%20requisites%20to%20ensure%20equality%20for%20marginalised%20sections%20and%20minority%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20must%20be%20remembered%20that%20women%20are%20not%20a%20homogenous%20group.%20True%20empowerment%20means%20ensuring%20women%20from%20diverse%20backgrounds%2C%20especially%20from%20marginalised%20and%20backward%20groups%2C%20have%20representation%20in%20parliament%20and%20state%20assemblies%2C%20rather%20than%20just%20those%20from%20political%20dynasties%20and%20privilege.%20The%20OBC%20population%20constitutes%20around%2041%25%20of%20the%20country's%20population%2C%20but%20somehow%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20does%20not%20consider%20it%20necessary%20to%20guarantee%20representation%20for%20this%20large%20population%20in%20the%20law-making%20chambers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%3A%20All%20For%20Women's%20Rights...Just%20Not%20Today%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWomen's%20active%20political%20participation%20is%20a%20fundamental%20prerequisite%20for%20achieving%20gender%20parity%20and%20true%20democracy.%20In%20a%20society%20characterized%20by%20tremendous%20inequalities%2C%20a%20mere%20token%20gesture%20from%20PM%20Modi%20is%20not%20the%20answer.%20Our%20politics%20should%20reflect%20and%20respond%20to%20the%20prevailing%20societal%20conditions%2C%20and%20strive%20to%20meet%20collective%20aspirations.%20In%20terms%20of%20its%20vision%20of%20implementation%2C%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20amendment%20is%2C%20at%20best%2C%20lousy%2C%20and%20at%20worst%2C%20mere%20exploitation%20of%20the%20women's%20rights%20agenda%20for%20the%20BJP's%20PR%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20India%20is%20to%20truly%20realise%20her%20aspirations%20in%20the%20Amritkaal%2C%20then%20women's%20reservation%20cannot%20wait%20any%20further.%20Every%20moment's%20delay%20is%20a%20step%20backwards%20and%20a%20lost%20opportunity.%20The%20implementation%20of%20the%20law%20in%20the%202024%20elections%20is%20an%20imperative.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Reena%20Gupta%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cb%3E%3Ci%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fb%3E%3Ci%3Eis%20an%20Advocate%20and%20National%20Spokesperson%20of%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696500000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fm2ukr428_pm-modi-women-reservation-bill_625x300_22_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbait-and-switch-bjps-charade-of-womens-quota-bill-4452425%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20re-introduction%20of%20the%20Women's%20Reservation%20Bill%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20government%2C%20after%20almost%20a%20decade%20in%20office%2C%20right%20before%20the%20upcoming%20general%20election%2C%20is%20no%20exception.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fbait-and-switch-bjps-charade-of-womens-quota-bill-4452425%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20extends%20tenure%20of%20SBI%20chairman%20Dinesh%20Khara%20until%20August%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696499877000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-07%2F20%2Ffull%2F1689851672-3236.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgovt-extends-tenure-of-sbi-chairman-dinesh-khara-until-august-2024-123100500653_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20is%20likely%20to%20issue%20an%20order%20to%20this%20effect%20shortly%2C%20the