Indian%20cricket%20but%20instead%20of%20exclusively%20leveraging%20their%20popularity%2C%20the%20ads%20served%20as%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%20role%20ODI%20cricket%20has%20specifically%20played%20in%20shaping%20their%20legacies%20%E2%80%93%20the%20statistical%20scale%20of%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%E2%80%99s%20batting%20records%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%E2%80%99s%20unforgettable%20double%20hundreds%2C%20or%20Virat%20Kohli%E2%80%99s%20astounding%20exploits%20while%20chasing%20totals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ads%20took%20no%20subtle%20measures%20in%20reminding%20fans%20that%20it%20is%20the%20nature%20and%20design%20of%20ODI%20cricket%20that%20allowed%20for%20some%20of%20their%20greatest%20living%20memories%20to%20be%20formed.%20It%20was%20as%20close%20as%20the%20broadcasters%20could%E2%80%99ve%20come%20to%20admitting%20the%20ODI%20format%20itself%20has%20considerably%20slipped%20out%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20cricket%20watching%20habits.%20And%20it%E2%80%99s%20obviously%20all%20the%20more%20concerning%20in%20a%20World%20Cup%20year%20as%20the%20quadrennial%20occasion%20still%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20flagship%20event%20this%20sport%20has%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResetting%20the%20fans%E2%80%99%20viewing%20preferences%20therefore%20was%20absolutely%20paramount%20and%20it%20further%20showed%20when%20the%20ICC%20themselves%20ensured%20their%20campaign%20for%20the%20World%20Cup%20too%20repeatedly%20headlined%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Eone-day%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20takes%20one%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20certain%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20kept%20saying%20through%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMsc6xy6a7e8%5C%22%3Eelaborate%20promo%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20was%20as%20cogent%20a%20giveaway%20as%20any%20that%20the%20format%20itself%20requires%20to%20be%20hard%20sold%20now%20before%20any%20specific%20series%20or%20tournament.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECompeting%20for%20space%20and%20attention%20against%20the%20far%20more%20constantly%20engaging%20and%20instantly%20gratifying%20T20s%2C%20the%2050-over%20game%20has%20long%20been%20facing%20a%20crisis%20of%20identity.%20While%20the%20Tests%20still%20serve%20the%20optics%20of%20elitist%20traditionalism%20against%20the%20marauding%20market%20forces%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20little%20incentive%20in%20championing%20a%20format%20that%E2%80%99s%20now%20uncontestably%20cricket%E2%80%99s%20unwanted%20inbetweener.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20it%20happened%20overnight%2C%20though.%20The%20narrative%20against%20ODI%20cricket%20has%20very%20steadily%20and%20smartly%20been%20allowed%20to%20build.%20From%20former%20icons%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhQ4rwZVS8Po%5C%22%3ERavi%20Shastri%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fodis-are-just-a-drag-now-the-format-is-kind-of-dying-wasim-akram-8047688%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3Done%252Dday%2520cricket%2520is%2520just%2Chours%2520the%2520game%2520is%2520over.%5C%22%3EWasim%20Akram%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20influential%20voices%20in%20cricket%20media%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espncricinfo.com%2Fstory%2Fmark-nicholas-mcc-president-odi-cricket-world-cups-1400719%5C%22%3EMark%20Nicholas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20everyone%20capable%20of%20reshaping%20public%20opinion%20has%20long%20concern-trolled%20over%20the%20future%20of%20ODIs.%20The%20%3Cem%3Econcern%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20plainly%20obvious%2C%20is%20but%20a%20cover%20for%20nudging%20the%20consumer%20toward%20accepting%20the%20primacy%20of%20the%20T20%20league%20model%20where%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20monetary%20interests%20are%20better%20served.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20selling%20digital%20and%20satellite%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwisden.com%2Fstories%2Fglobal-t20-leagues%2Findian-premier-league-2022%2Fexplained-ipl-gigantic-record-6-2-billion-media-rights-deal-thats-bigger-than-the-epl%5C%22%3Ebroadcast%20rights%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20attracting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fsports%2Ftata-takes-over-ipl-sponsorship-crown-from-vivo%2Farticleshow%2F88844097.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ecommercial%20sponsorships%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20dominance%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20today%20is%20unrivalled.%20It%20is%20hands%20down%20the%20foremost%20property%20in%20cricket%20and%20on%20potential%20competes%20with%20the%20biggest%20brands%20in%20European%20and%20American%20sporting%20markets.%20It%20has%20encouraged%20the%20Indian%20capital%20to%20spill%20over%20and%20invest%20in%20leagues%20in%20other%20countries.%20It%E2%80%99s%20hoped%20that%20it%20will%20eventually%20create%20a%20monopolistic%20ecosystem%20where%20the%20cricket%20calendar%20is%20primarily%20occupied%20by%20these%20leagues%20and%20the%20international%20game%20(effectively%20the%20other%20two%20formats)%20struggles%20to%20find%20room%20to%20host%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20administrators%20and%20big%20capital%2C%20though%2C%20are%20not%20the%20only%20beneficiaries%20of%20cricket%20making%20a%20decisive%20pivot%20toward%20T20%20leagues.%20It%20also%20generates%20significantly%20greater%20earning%20potential%20for%20parallel%20economies%20feeding%20off%20cricket%20%E2%80%93%20more%20coaching%20and%20consulting%20gigs%20for%20former%20players%2C%20professional%20partnerships%20for%20firms%20in%20the%20business%20of%20data%20analytics%2C%20higher%20engagement%20numbers%20for%20social%20media%20influencers%2C%20and%20a%20much%20larger%20platform%20for%20consumer%20brands%20to%20push%20their%20new%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBasically%20every%20element%20that%20drew%20excessive%20amounts%20of%20money%20once%20every%20four%20years%20for%20what%20was%20perceived%20to%20be%20the%20ultimate%20celebration%20of%20cricket%20is%20now%20available%20to%20the%20markets%20every%20year%20for%20a%20two-month%20long%20window.%20The%20uniqueness%20and%20excitability%20of%20a%20World%20Cup%20has%20naturally%20taken%20a%20hit%20in%20the%20process%20and%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20has%20lived%20up%20to%20its%20reputation%20as%20an%20imprudent%20organisation%20at%20handling%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESomewhere%20in%20late%202018%2C%20the%20governing%20body%20of%20cricket%20came%20up%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icc-cricket.com%2Fmedia-releases%2F917529%5C%22%3Eidea%20to%20rename%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20very%20successful%20T20%20property%20from%20WorldT20%20to%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20The%20rechristening%2C%20it%20was%20told%2C%20was%20done%20with%20the%20idea%20to%20use%20T20s%20as%20a%20vehicle%20to%20further%20globalise%20the%20game.%20No%20one%20knows%20what%20globalising%20cricket%20truly%20entails%20but%20the%20move%20effectively%20compromised%20the%20sanctity%20of%20what%20a%20World%20Cup%20stood%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20singular%20standout%20event%20that%20everyone%20remained%20in%20anticipation%20of%2C%20it%20now%20became%20another%20throwaway%20ICC%20event%20that%E2%80%99s%20scheduled%20every%20year.%20Every%20serious%20media%20organisation%20started%20adding%20%E2%80%98ODI%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%9850-over%E2%80%99%20as%20qualifiers%20now%20to%20identify%20the%20World%20Cup%20to%20separate%20it%20from%20a%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20Far%20from%20being%20the%20biggest%20showdown%20tournament%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20even%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20World%20Cup%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThink%20of%20the%20eight-year-olds%20only%20just%20warming%20up%20to%20cricket%20in%202023.%20How%20exactly%20are%20they%20supposed%20to%20fathom%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20when%20there%20was%20one%20held%20only%20last%20year%20and%20there%E2%80%99ll%20be%20another%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20a%20few%20more%20months%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20%E2%80%98World%20Cup%E2%80%99%20has%20a%20certain%20universality%20to%20it.%20Across%20sports%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20widely%20accepted%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20event%20on%20offer%20and%20starting%20to%20loosely%20call%20tournaments%20in%20a%20condensed%20format%20that%20are%20held%20every%20other%20year%20World%20Cups%20is%20a%20serious%20disservice%20to%20the%20name%20and%20the%20sentiment%20it%E2%80%99s%20meant%20to%20evoke.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20foresight%20is%20not%20exactly%20the%20ICC%E2%80%99s%20strongest%20suit%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20be%20completely%20dismissive%20of%20the%20suspicion%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20perhaps%20done%20by%20design%20with%20the%20intention%20to%20steadily%20phase%20ODIs%20out%20of%20the%20sport.%20In%20fact%2C%20one%20of%20the%20more%20bizarre%20suggestions%20lately%20has%20been%20to%20stop%20playing%20ODIs%20outside%20World%20Cups.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20simply%20assumes%20players%20will%20on%20their%20own%20adjust%20to%20the%20rhythm%20of%2050-over%20cricket%20every%20four%20years%20while%20completely%20severing%20ties%20with%20it%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20time.%20There%E2%80%99s%20another%20implication%20here%20that%20ODIs%20can%20simply%20be%20approached%20as%20an%20extended%20version%20of%20T20s%20and%20aren%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20a%20format%20with%20its%20own%20mechanics%20and%20specificities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20such%20absurd%20recommendations%20find%20a%20platform%20from%20respectable%20publications%20and%20are%20regularly%20amplified%3B%20to%20the%20point%20that%20the%20consensus%20over%20the%20snubbing%20of%20an%20entire%20format%20is%20all%20but%20reached.%20There%20is%20already%20a%20demand%20for%20enhancing%20the%20length%20of%20an%20IPL%20season%20and%20with%20the%20Indian%20capital%20funding%20as%20many%20as%20four%20other%20feeder%20leagues%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20other%20formats%20are%20going%20to%20find%20fewer%20and%20fewer%20takers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20this%20rather%20oversimplistic%20argument%20of%20the%20markets%20ultimately%20serving%20what%20the%20consumer%20wants%20to%20see%20on%20their%20TV%20sets%20and%20smartphones.%20The%20demand-supply%20dynamics%20in%20reality%2C%20though%2C%20are%20about%20cutting%20down%20on%20the%20consumer%E2%80%99s%20choices%20and%20artificially%20creating%20a%20sense%20of%20demand%20for%20something%20over%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20sustained%20and%20concerted%20effort%20at%20changing%20the%20viewing%20habits%20of%20the%20cricket-loving%20public.%20The%20ODIs%20have%20been%20allowed%20to%20be%20perceived%20as%20an%20inconsequential%20afterthought%20by%20sporadic%20scheduling%2C%20with%20the%20best%20players%20often%20skipping%20games%20while%20over-enthusiastic%20commentators%20relentlessly%20tell%20viewers%20that%20they%20do%20not%20like%20watching%20this%20format%20anymore%20and%20that%20it%20must%20make%20more%20room%20for%20franchise%20leagues.%20The%20consumer%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20is%20a%20prisoner%20of%20his%20need%20to%20have%20some%20form%20of%20entertainment%20on%20his%20screen%20and%20will%20eventually%20settle%20for%20what%E2%80%99s%20dished%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20deterrent%20to%20actualise%20this%20paradigm%20shift%20however%2C%20is%20the%20fact%20the%20population%20that%20advertisers%20mean%20to%20serve%20through%20cricket%20in%20large%20part%20consists%20of%20millennials.%20Having%20grown%20up%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20they%20continue%20to%20have%20some%20nostalgic%20fondness%20for%20World%20Cups.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20to%20wipe%20out%20a%20whole%20format%2C%20therefore%2C%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20as%20rapid%20as%20many%20would%E2%80%99ve%20liked%20and%20this%20World%20Cup%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20determining%20how%20soon%20that%20final%20pivot%20takes%20place.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20like%20there%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20another%20World%20Cup%20after%20this%20one%20%E2%80%93%20two%20more%20have%20already%20been%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20it%20fails%20to%20create%20the%20desired%20impact%20over%20the%20next%20month%20and%20a%20half%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20highly%20likely%20that%20the%20next%20two%20will%20be%20played%20only%20because%20they%20absolutely%20have%20to%20be.%20Cricket%20shall%20transform%20into%20a%20completely%20unrecognisable%20version%20of%20itself%20where%20primacy%20squarely%20lies%20with%20T20%20leagues%20around%20the%20year%20and%20once%20in%20a%20while%20Australia%2C%20England%20and%20India%20play%20an%20odd%20Test%20series%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20impossible%20to%20be%20able%20to%20pointedly%20tell%20the%20time%20in%20the%20future%20when%20this%20shift%20will%20take%20place%2C%20but%20it%20looks%20increasingly%20certain%20that%20when%20it%20does%2C%20few%20will%20care.%20But%20it%E2%80%99s%20vital%20this%20piece%20of%20cricket%20history%20be%20written%20accurately.%20The%20people%20never%20demanded%20for%20the%20one-day%20cricket%20to%20be%20snubbed.%20It%20was%20a%20self-serving%20coterie%20of%20administrators%2C%20broadcasters%2C%20and%20big%20capital%20that%20found%20a%20way%20to%20mint%20more%20money%20with%20less%20amount%20of%20cricket%20per%20game.%20And%20while%20doing%20that%2C%20they%20simply%20pretended%20to%20be%20speaking%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696498235000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05144016%2FF7mL_1LXkAAXuJn.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fone-final-world-cup-before-cricket-makes-the-inevitable-pivot%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Competing%20for%20space%20and%20attention%20against%20the%20far%20more%20constantly%20engaging%20and%20instantly%20gratifying%20T20s%2C%20the%2050-over%20game%20has%20long%20been%20facing%20a%20crisis%20of%20identity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fone-final-world-cup-before-cricket-makes-the-inevitable-pivot%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I