%20the%20entire%20eVTOL%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20NASA%20research%20pilot%20Wayne%20Ringelberg%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20research%20will%20include%20a%20focus%20on%20handling%20qualities%20evaluation%20tools%2C%20autonomy%2C%20and%20airspace%20integration%2C%20which%20is%20all%20needed%20research%20to%20push%20the%20industry%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJoby's%20eVTOL%20is%20not%20the%20only%20historic%20aircraft%20to%20operate%20at%20Edwards%2C%20with%20both%20the%20first%20American%20fighter%20jet%20and%20the%20first%20supersonic%20aircraft%20setting%20records%20at%20the%20base.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20three%20prototype%20Bell%20P-59s.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651c75a542ecf94db4771357%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20three%20prototype%20Bell%20P-59s.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPowered%20by%20two%20General%20Electric%20turbojets%2C%20the%20American-made%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalmuseum.af.mil%2FVisit%2FMuseum-Exhibits%2FFact-Sheets%2FDisplay%2FArticle%2F195780%2Fbell-p-59b-airacomet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBell%20P-59%20Airacomet%20fighter%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20its%20world%20debut%20in%20October%201942%20when%20the%20first%20of%20three%20prototypes%20flew%20over%20what%20is%20now%20known%20as%20Edwards%20Air%20Force%20Base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20never%20saw%20combat%2C%20it%20was%20invaluable%20for%20training%20during%20World%20War%20II%20and%20helped%20the%20US%20gather%20data%20to%20make%20better-performing%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconcorde-supersonic-jet-history-2018-10%5C%22%3Esupersonic%20Bell%20X-1%20broke%20the%20sound%20barrier%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20th