5C%22804%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20Air%20Force%20personnel%20with%20Joby's%20experimental%20eVTOL.%3Cp%3EJoby%20Aviation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Joby%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20its%20eVTOL%20test%20flights%20have%20been%20remotely%20piloted%20from%20a%20ground%20station%20%26quot%3Busing%20state-of-the-art%20communications%20technology%20and%20software.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20manufacturer%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20it%20is%20finally%20putting%20a%20pilot%20in%20the%20cockpit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20four%20pilots%20have%20flown%20its%20electric%20pre-production%20prototype%20aircraft%2C%20who%20completed%20%26quot%3Ba%20series%20of%20initial%20tests%20that%20included%20free%20thrustborne%20hovers%20and%20forward%20transitions%20to%20semi-thrustborne%20flight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20flights%2C%20which%20were%20performed%20at%20Joby's%20production%20plant%20in%20California%2C%20assessed%20things%20like%20aircraft%20handling%20and%20pilot%20control%20interfaces.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221067%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joby%20prototype%20eVTOL%20at%20the%20facility.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F651c7a872ce014759e740e0b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoby%20prototype%20eVTOL%20at%20its%20production%20facility%20in%20California.%3Cp%3EJoby%20Aviation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pilots%20performed%20things%20like%20vertical%20takeoff%2C%20accelerating%2C%20transitioning%20from%20hover%20to%20forward%20flight%2C%20deceleration%2C%20and%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20helped%20design%20and%20test%20flight%20controls%20for%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20aircraft%2C%20including%20all%20three%20variants%20of%20the%20F-35%20Joint%20Strike%20Fighter%2C%20nothing%20compares%20to%20the%20simplicity%20and%20grace%20of%20the%20Joby%20aircraft%2C%26quot%