%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22trains%40insider.com%20(Taylor%20Rains)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffirst-electric-air-taxi-delivered-to-us-joby-evtol-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Conference%20Empowered%20200%20Students%20With%20Unique%20Ideas%20on%20Climate%20Change%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20sponsored%20by%20Mobius%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%C2%A0woman%20starts%20menstruating%2C%20she%20will%20be%20bleeding%20once%20a%20month%20for%20approximately%2035%20to%2040%20years%2C%20using%20approximately%2010%2C000%20sanitary%20napkins%20during%20her%20lifetime%2C%20which%20end%20up%20in%20landfills.%20The%20plastic%20used%20in%20these%20pads%20is%20non-biodegradable%20and%20can%20lead%20to%20health%20and%20environmental%20hazards.%20According%20to%20Menstrual%20Health%20Alliance%20India%2C%20one%20sanitary%20pad%20could%20take%20500%20to%20800%20years%20to%20decompose.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecognising%20this%20massive%20problem%2C%20a%20team%20of%20students%20from%20the%20Iconic%20School%2C%20Bhopal%2C%20started%20looking%20for%20a%20solution.%20They%20decided%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321703%2Fiit-material-scientists-innovate-biodegradable-super-absorbent-sheets-for-sanitary-pads%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebiodegradable%20sanitary%20pads%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20resources%20they%20had%20in%20hand%20through%20their%20project%20BacWP.%20They%20used%20water%20hyacinth%2C%20bagasse%20and%20papaya%20fibre%20to%20make%20sanitary%20napkins%20while%20ensuring%20menstrual%20hygiene%20and%20proper%20waste%20decomposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20successfully%20demonstrated%20that%20students%20and%20young%20people%20can%20use%20their%20education%20to%20make%20a%20positive%20impact%20on%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20project%20received%20recognition%20at%20the%20Youth%20for%20Earth%20Campaign%202023%20%E2%80%94%20a%20platform%20for%20young%20changemakers%20to%20showcase%20their%20innovations.%20Conducted%20by%20Mobius%20Foundation%20in%20partnership%20with%20The%20Climate%20Project%20Foundation%2C%20200%20youth%20groups%20participated%20in%20this%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETen%20of%20the%20best%20projects%20%E2%80%94%20made%20on%20the%20theme%20%E2%80%98United%20Nations%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goal%2013%3A%20Climate%20Action%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20were%20rewarded%20at%20the%20fifth%20International%20Conference%20on%20Sustainability%20Education%20(ICSE).%20Five%20of%20these%20were%20awarded%20in%20the%20youth%20category%20(schools)%20and%20five%20in%20the%20senior%20category%2C%20which%20included%20colleges%2C%20universities%20and%20independent%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EProject%20BacWP%20won%20the%20second%20prize%20of%20Rs%2030%2C000%20in%20the%20youth%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202274px)%20100vw%2C%202274px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC_9864_11zon-1696496492.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dignitaries%20at%20the%205th%20International%20Conference%20on%20Sustainability%20Education%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC_9864_11zon-1696496492.jpg%202274w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC_9864_11zon-1696496492-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC_9864_11zon-1696496492-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC_9864_11zon-1696496492-768x511.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC_9864_11zon-1696496492-1536x1022.jpg%201536w%2C%2