d%20after%20a%20cloudburst%20over%20Lhonak%20Lake%20in%20north%20Sikkim%20resulted%20in%20a%20flash%20flood%20in%20the%20Teesta%20river.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20is%20%E2%80%9Creeling%20under%20a%20huge%20disaster%E2%80%9D%20said%20Sunita%20Khatiwara%2C%20a%20native%20of%20south%20Sikkim%20who%20is%20currently%20a%20project%20officer%20at%20the%20Forest%20and%20Environment%20Department%20in%20Gangtok.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReports%20are%20coming%20in%20that%20a%20Glacial%20Lake%20Outburst%20Flood%20(GLOF)%20%E2%80%93%20triggered%20by%20the%20cloudburst%20above%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20glacial%20lake%20in%20North%20Sikkim%20%E2%80%93%20caused%20the%20Chungthang%20Dam%20breach%20and%20the%20flooding%20downstream%20of%20the%20Teesta%20river%20basin%2C%20Khatiwara%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20flood%20was%20exacerbated%20by%20the%20release%20of%20water%20from%20the%20Chungthang%20dam%2C%20according%20to%20some%20locals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArmy%20vehicles%20parked%20near%20Bardang%2C%20close%20to%20Singtam%2C%20were%20swept%20away.%20Twenty%20three%20personnel%20were%20reported%20missing%2C%20and%20some%20vehicles%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20submerged%20under%20the%20slush.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Army%E2%80%99s%20Eastern%20Command%20issued%20a%20statement%20indicating%20that%20some%20establishments%20along%20Lachen%20Valley%20have%20been%20affected.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20of%20Khatiwara%E2%80%99s%20immediate%20relatives%20living%20downstream%20of%20the%20flood%20areas%20are%20currently%20in%20relief%20camps%20because%20their%20houses%20are%20flooded%2C%20she%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Power%20cuts%20are%20a%20concern%20in%20the%20town%2C%20and%20so%20is%20poor%20data%20networks%2C%20which%20make%20communication%20difficult.%20Apart%20from%20these%2C%20incessant%20rain%20is%20delaying%20rescue%20and%20relief%20work%20too%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAssistant%20District%20Magistrate%20of%20Mangan%2C%20Sonam%20Tashi%2C%20said%20mobile%20towers%20may%20have%20been%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Hazardous%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F10106049.2020.1869332%3Fscroll%3Dtop%26needAccess%3Dtrue%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estudy%20in%202020%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20listed%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20lake%20as%20among%20the%2010%20lakes%20posing%20the%20highest%20GLOF%20threats%20among%20the%2036%20glacial%20lakes%20in%20the%20North%20Sikkim%20that%20the%20study%20shortlisted%20as%20%E2%80%9Chazardous%E2%80%9D%20based%20on%20several%20geological%20parameters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Lake%20has%20also%20been%20expanding%20over%20the%20years%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS2666033422000181%23bib13%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eseveral%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20studies%20show.%20The%20culprit%3A%20climate%20change.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20temperatures%20rise%20due%20to%20global%20warming%2C%20glaciers%20are%20retreating%2C%20or%20getting%20smaller.%20In%20turn%2C%20the%20lakes%20attached%20to%20them%20%E2%80%93%20glacial%20lakes%20%E2%80%93%20are%20increasing%20in%20area.%20One%20study%20found%20that%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20Glacial%20Lake%20in%20the%20Upper%20Teesta%20Basin%20is%20growing%20at%20an%20average%20aerial%20expansion%20of%200.03%20square%20km%20per%20year.%20The%202020%20study%20found%20that%20the%20Lhonak%20Lake%20increased%20in%20size%20by%200.205%20square%20km%20between%202000%20and%202018%20alone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05131444%2FScreenshot-2023-10-05-at-1.14.37-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221196%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05131444%2FScreenshot-2023-10-05-at-1.14.37-PM.png%201196w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05131444%2FScreenshot-2023-10-05-at-1.14.37-PM-300x147.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05131444%2FScreenshot-2023-10-05-at-1.14.37-PM-1024x503.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-678398%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22588%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Lhonak%20Lake%20increased%20in%20size%20by%200.205%20sq%20km%20between%202000%20and%202018.%20Photo%3A%20Nazimul%20Islam%20%26amp%3B%20Priyank%20Pravin%20Patel%20(2021)%3A%20Inventory%20and%20GLOF%20hazard%20assessment%20of%20glacial%20lakes%20in%20the%20Sikkim%20Himalayas%2C%20India%2C%20Geocarto%20International%2C%20DOI%3A%2010.1080%2F10106049.2020.1869332%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20warmer%20temperatures%20are%20also%20causing%20the%20formation%20of%20more%20glacial%20lakes%20in%20the%20upper%20reaches%20of%20the%20Teesta%20river%20in%20the%20district%20of%20Northern%20Sikkim.%20The%202020%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Ffull%2F10.1080%2F10106049.2020.1869332%3Fscroll%3Dtop%26needAccess%3Dtrue%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estudy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20found%20that%20203%20new%20lakes%20have%20formed%20in%20the%20region%20between%202000%20and%202018.%20Of%20these%2C%2082%20were%20born%20between%202011%20and%202018%20alone.%20The%20overall%20area%20under%20lakes%20in%20North%20Sikkim%20has%20increased%20by%20a%20shocking%206.9%20square%20km%20between%202000%20to%202018%20(a%20rise%20of%2037.5%25).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0169555X21001914%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Estudy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%202021%20mapped%20infrastructure%20exposed%20to%20GLOFs%20in%20the%20Teesta%20valley%20and%20found%20that%20%E2%80%9Cmany%20settlements%20and%20assets%20located%20along%20the%20river%20channel%20at%20Chungthang%20are%20potentially%20exposed%20to%20future%20GLOFs%2C%20indicating%20the%20need%20to%20conduct%20a%20full%20environmental%20impact%20assessment%20and%20potentially%20undertake%20GLOF%20risk%20mitigation%20measures%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EImages%20released%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fisro%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40isro%3C%2Fa%3E%20confirming%20that%20South%20Lhonak%20lake%20burst.%20So%20this%20is%20confirmed%20to%20be%20a%20GLOF%20event%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETeesta%20III%20hydroelectric%20project%20in%20Chungthang%2C%20Sikkim%20was%20overwhelmed%20by%20a%20GLOF%20event.%20Sobering%2C%20all%20those%20years%20of%20paper%20warnings%20come%20true%20in%20real%20life.%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F55sLGs6VQv%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F55sLGs6VQv%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Anand%20Sankar%20(%40kalapian_)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkalapian_%2Fstatus%2F1709614242318741912%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%204%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20Teesta%20River%20flows%20through%20Sikkim%20and%20West%20Bengal%20before%20entering%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENumerous%20houses%2C%20hotels%20and%20tourist%20facilities%20are%20understood%20to%20be%20affected.%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20Siliguri%20and%20Jalpaiguri%20districts%20are%20also%20part%20of%20the%20red%20alert%20that%20has%20been%20issued.%20Evacuations%20are%20in%20progress%20for%20residents%20living%20near%20the%20river%20and%20in%20hill%20areas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20rainfall%20has%20slightly%20decreased%2C%20communication%20remains%20disrupted%20in%20a%20significant%20portions%20of%20North%20Sikkim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20migrant%20labourers%20and%20locals%20living%20near%20the%20river%20are%20swept%20away.%20The%20administration%20and%20the%20army%20are%20trying%20to%20rescue%20people.%20We%20can%20not%20estimate%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20loss%20now.%20This%20is%20a%20seismic%20zone%2C%20prone%20to%20earthquakes%20and%20landslides.%20We%20need%20to%20introspect%20our%20handling%20of%20the%20Himalayas%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Navin%20Kiran%2C%20a%20Gangtok%20based%20socio%20political%20activist%20currently%20in%20the%20affected%20zone%2C%20Rangpo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProjects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Chungthang%20Hydro-Dam%20is%20a%20crucial%20component%20of%20the%201200-megawatt%20Teesta%20Stage%20III%20Hydro%20Electric%20Project%2C%20which%20was%20developed%20by%20Teesta%20Urja.%20This%20project%20was%20commissioned%20in%202017%2C%20at%20an%20estimated%20cost%20of%20Rs%2014%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20construction%20process%20for%20this%20project%20had%20involved%20blasting%20activities%20and%20the%20boring%20of%20tunnels.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20Kedarnath%20disaster%2C%20tourism%20operators%20in%20Sikkim%20had%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20filed%20an%20RTI%20to%20understand%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20dams%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20government%20had%20said%20that%20out%20of%20the%2012%20dams%20in%20Sikkim%2C%20seven%20are%20in%20a%20vulnerable%20condition%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20environment%20activist%20Mukut%20Biswas%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Prameya%20Foundation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEnvironmentalists%20have%20been%20expressing%20serious%20concerns%20about%20the%20construction%20of%20large-scale%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20the%20Eastern%20Himalayas%2C%20particularly%20the%20building%20of%20multiple%20dams.%20This%20region%20is%20situated%20in%20seismic%20zones%20IV%20and%20V%2C%20which%20are%20known%20to%20be%20highly%20susceptible%20to%20earthquakes.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20have%20also%20been%20warnings%20from%20ecologists%20regarding%20the%20ongoing%2045%20km-long%20Sivok-Rangpo%20rail%20project.%20This%20railway%20project%20aims%20to%20connect%20the%20Sivok%20railway%20station%20in%20Darjeeling%20district%20of%20West%20Bengal%2C%20to%20Rangpo%20in%20East%20Sikkim%20and%20involves%20the%20construction%20of%20several%20tunnels.%20One%20of%20the%20construction%20train%20stations%20under%20construction%20was%20damaged%20in%20the%20flash%20floods.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%20on%20ecology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20South%20Lhonak%20glacial%20lake%20was%20already%20known%20to%20be%20extremely%20vulnerable%20and%20the%20ecological%20impacts%20of%20this%20disaster%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cunprecedented%E2%80%9D%2C%20Khatiwara%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20GLOF%20occurred%20in%20the%20Kanchendzonga%20Biosphere%20Reserve%2C%20which%20is%20home%20to%20many%20rare%20and%20endangered%20wildlife%2C%20the%20wildlife%20biologist%20noted.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAn%20assessment%20is%20already%20underway%20and%20all%20concerned%20officers%20have%20been%20instructed%20by%20forest%20officials%20to%20conduct%20a%20detailed%20assessment%2C%E2%80%9D%20Khatiwara%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Reserve%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20is%20home%20to%20the%20species%20including%20the%20snow%20leopard%20and%20more%20than%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthreatenedtaxa.org%2Findex.php%2FJoTT%2Farticle%2Fview%2F3728%2F4317%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E35%20species%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20rhododendron%2C%20the%20state%20tree%20of%20Sikkim.%20The%20Reserve%20was%20added%20to%20the%20list%20of%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20Sites%20in%202016%2C%20and%20is%20the%20first%20%E2%80%9Cmixed%E2%80%9D%20heritage%20site%20in%20India%20because%20it%20meets%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwhc.unesco.org%2Fen%2Flist%2F1513%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eboth%20cultural%20and%20natural%20heritage%20criteria%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Indigenous%20communities%20including%20the%20Lepchas%20and%20Bhutias%20consider%20Mount%20Khangchendzonga%2C%20which%20lies%20within%20the%20Reserve%2C%20as%20sacred.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20Aathira%20Perinchery)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696495396000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05140822%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-10-04-at-7.12.12-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsikkim-glacial-lake-outburst-flood-impact-ecology%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20study%20in%202020%20listed%20the%20South%20Lhonak%20lake%20as%20among%20the%2010%20lakes%20posing%20the%20highest%20GLOF%20threats%20among%20the%2036%20glacial%20lakes%20in%20the%20North%20Sikkim%20that%20the%20study%20shortlisted%20as%20%E2%80%9Chazardous%E2%80%9D%20based%20on%20several%20geological%20parameters.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsikkim-glacial-lake-outburst-flood-impact-ecology%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden's%20dog%20Commander%20leaves%20White%20House%20after