0Bhushan's%20novel%2C%20Escape%20to%20Nowhere%2C%20Bhardwaj%20and%20Rohan%20Narula's%20screenplay%20turns%20the%20material%20into%20an%20intriguing%2C%20riveting%20drama%20that%20abides%20by%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20genre%20without%20letting%20itself%20be%20totally%20hamstrung%20by%20the%20limitations%20that%20trid-and%20tested%20devices%20often%20impose.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKhufiya%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(which%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20Bhardwaj's%20Agatha%20Christie%20murder%20mystery%20series%2C%20Charlie%20Chopra%20%26amp%3B%20the%20Mystery%20of%20Solang%20Valley)%20is%20probably%2C%20at%20least%20on%20the%20face%20of%20it%2C%20one%20of%20the%20very%20few%20straightforward%20genre%20films%20that%20he%20has%20made.%20Even%20his%20misfires%20-%20in%20fact%2C%20especially%20his%20misfires%20-%20have%20been%20marked%20by%20the%20sort%20of%20fearlessness%20that%20Mumbai%20filmmakers%20working%20within%20mainstream%20parameters%20aren't%20usually%20known%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBe%20it%20a%20Shakespearean%20adaptation%20(%3Cem%3EMaqbool%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%3Cem%3E%20Omkara%2C%20Haider%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20a%20crime%20drama%20(%3Cem%3EKaminey%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20a%20pitch-dark%20comedy%20%3Cem%3E(7%20Khoon%20Maaf%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20a%20politico-romantic%20period%20saga%20%3Cem%3E(Rangoon%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20an%20acutely%20tangential%20allegory%20(%3Cem%3EMatru%20ki%20Bijlee%20Ka%20Mandola%2C%20Pataakha%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20or%20even%20a%20children's%20film%20(%3Cem%3EMakdee%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20his%20directorial%20debut)%2C%20Bhardwaj%20has%20never%20been%20a%20slave%20to%20narrative-form%20constrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FByojhBwG_-E%3Fsi%3DlJs4G1xpWKDoN94n%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20if%C2%A0%3Cem%3EKhufiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20employs%20established%20storytelling%20conventions%20to%20craft%20a%20film%20that%20is%20as%20interested%20in%20studying%20character%20traits%20as%20in%20juggling%20plot%20details%20to%20engender%20tension%20and%20suspense%2C%20it%20is%20only%20to%20be%20expected.%20Directed%20with%20a%20commendable%20lightness%20of%20touch%20and%20magnificently%20well-acted%2C%20the%20sure-handed%20film%20delivers%20on%20all%20fronts%20without%20calling%20attention%20to%20its%20exceptional%20technical%20attributes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDo%20we%20know%20any%20Mumbai%20espionage%20thriller%20that%20starts%20with%20a%20reference%20to%20something%20as%20insignificant%20and%20yet%20as%20evocative%20as%20a%20mole%20on%20a%20woman's%20jugular%20notch%2C%20that%20delicate%20curve%20in%20middle%20of%20the%20collarbone%2C%20a%20conceit%20and%20an%20image%20that%20instantly%20evokes%20both%20mystery%20and%20sensuality%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20very%20next%20thing%20that%C2%A0%3Cem%3EKhufiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20does%20is%20go%20for%20the%20jugular%20and%20spring%20a%20'mole'%20upon%20us%20-%20both%20of%20which%20are%20delivered%20matter-of-factly.%20An%20undercover%20agent%20is%20murdered%20-%20an%20act%20committed%20with%20absolute%20impunity%20and%20fuelled%20by%20a%20leak%20from%20within%20India's%20intelligence%20network%20-%20at%20a%20Bangladeshi%20brigadier's%20birthday%20bash.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20identity%20of%20the%20prime%20suspect%20is%20revealed%20early%20on%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20film%20focuses%20on%20R%26amp%3BAW's%20mission%20to%20bring%20the%20absconding%20traitor%20to%20book.%20The%20operation%20-%20codenamed%20Brutus%2C%20a%20byword%20for%20betrayal%20in%20the%20universe%20of%20William%20Shakespeare's%20great%20tragedies%20-%20is%20led%20by%20Krishna%20Mehra%20(Tabu)%2C%20KM%20to%20agency%20insiders%20and%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKM's%20life%20is%20shrouded%20in%20as%20much%20mystery%20as%20the%20motives%20of%20the%20treacherous%20Ravi%20Mohan%20(Ali%20Fazal)%2C%20a%20modestly%20paid%20Indian%20secret%20service%20operative%20who%20has%20a%20lifestyle%20that%20does%20not%20match%20his%20known%20sources%20of%20income.%20Nothing%20about%20the%20steely%20lady%20charged%20with%20unmasking%20the%20puppeteer%20behind%20the%20puppet%20is%20spelled%20out%20in%20black%20and%20white.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGreys%20-%20not%20outlined%20in%20simplistic%20moral%20terms%20-%20dominate%20her%20existence.%20The%20seasoned%20spy%20is%20divorced%20from%20her%20husband%20Shashank%20(Atul%20Kulkarni%20in%20a%20cameo)%2C%20has%20an%20uneasy%20relationship%20with%20her%2019-year-old%20son%20Vikram%20(Meet%20Vohra)%2C%20an%20actor%20and%20musician%20who%20feels%20that%20his%20mother%20hides%20too%20much%20from%20him%20and%20possesses%20the%20temerity%20to%20cross%20the%20line%20when%20a%20situation%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20turn%20of%20the%20millennium%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20after%20the%20Kargil%20conflict%2C%20KM%2C%20during%20a%20stint%20in%20the%20Indian%20high%20commission%20in%20Dhaka%2C%20recruits%20a%20walk-in%20applicant%2C%20Heena%20Rehman%20(Azmeri%20Haque%20Badhon)%2C%20and%20develops%20a%20special%20bond%20with%20her%2C%20a%20fact%20that%20drives%20her%20subsequent%20actions%20that%20see%20her%20travel%20from%20Delhi%20to%20wintry%20South%20Dakota%20(a%20Canadian%20location%20stands%20in%20for%20the%20American%20Midwest).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERavi%20Mohan's%20life%20is%20apparently%20far%20less%20remarkable.%20He%20has%20a%20desk%20job%20in%20R%26amp%3BAW's%20headquarters%20in%20Delhi%2C%20lives%20with%20his%20mother%20Lalita%20(Navnindra%20Behl)%2C%20wife%20Charu%20(Wamiqa%20Gabbi)%20and%20primary%20school%20student-son%20Kunal%20(Swastik%20Tiwari)%20and%20drives%20a%20nondescript%20hatchback.%20But%20it%20is%20revealed%20early%20in%20the%20film%20that%20there%20is%20more%20to%20the%20man%20than%20meets%20the%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERavi%20and%20his%20mother%20are%20followers%20of%20Yaar%20Jogiya%20(Indian%20Ocean's%20Rahul%20Ram%2C%20who%20lends%20his%20voice%20and%20performative%20energy%20to%20the%20film)%2C%20a%20new-age%20spiritualist%20who%20croons%20Kabir-inspired%20songs%20to%20communicate%20with%20his%20flock.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKhufiya%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20however%2C%20is%20not%20so%20much%20about%20the%20men%20that%20we%20encounter%20on%20th%20screen%20-%20besides%20Ravi%2C%20Yaar%20Jogiya%20and%20Shashank%2C%20there%20is%20Jeev%20(Ashish%20Vidyarthi)%2C%20KM's%20boss%20-%20as%20it%20is%20about%20the%20women.%20And%20that%20includes%20Ravi's%20ageing%20and%20assertive%20mother%2C%20a%20matron%20capable%20of%20shocking%20acts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERavi's%20wife%2C%20dutiful%20and%20aware%20of%20her%20multiple%20roles%20as%20mother%2C%20wife%20and%20daughter-in-law%2C%20has%20a%20side%20to%20her%20that%20makes%20it%20possible%20for%20the%20spies%20tailing%20her%20husband%20that%20she%20is%20not%20only%20in%20the%20know%20of%20the%20man's%20betrayal%20of%20his%20nation%20but%20also%20a%20willing%20accomplice.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bangladeshi%20agent%20working%20for%20India's%20spy%20agency%2C%20Heena%20Rehman%2C%20is%20seemingly%20the%20least%20important%20of%20the%20three%20women%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20Khufiya%20but%20she%20is%20just%20as%20alluring%20and%20mystifying%20as%20the%20other%20two.%20Her%20presence%20-%20and%20absence%20-%20make%20this%20a%20love%20story%20and%20a%20tale%20of%20revenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sprightly%20Charu%20has%20a%20fixation%20with%20songs%20from%20Jawani%20Diwani%2C%20a%20Hindi%20film%20from%20half%20a%20century%20ago%2C%20and%20lets%20her%20hair%20down%20in%20more%20ways%20than%20one%20when%20nobody%20is%20watching%20and%20sways%20with%20gay%20abandon%20to%20the%20numbers%2C%20one%20peppy%2C%20the%20other%20steamy.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20by%20a%20fair%20distance%2C%20the%20pivotal%20figure%20in%20Khufiya%20is%20KM%2C%20an%20enigmatic%20secret%20agent%20whose%20secrets%20transcend%20the%20professional%20sphere%20and%20embrace%20her%20personal%20life.%20She%20is%20both%20a%20sleuth%20-%20in%20one%20stray%20scene%2C%20we%20see%20her%20sitting%20on%20a%20park%20bench%20reading%20an%20Agatha%20Christie%20book%20-%20and%20a%20key%20player%20in%20the%20story%20that%20she%20is%20out%20to%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20ever-reliable%20Tabu%20leading%20the%20way%2C%20the%20performances%20are%20right%20out%20of%20the%20top%20drawer.%20%3Cem%3EKhufiya%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20another%20fluttering%20feather%20in%20Wamiqa%20Gabbi's%20cap.%20She%20is%20consistently%20on%20top%20of%20her%20character%2C%20which%20undergoes%20a%20dramatic%20tonal%20shift%20halfway%20through%20the%20film.%20She%20aces%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAzmeri%20Haque%20Badhon%20(lead%20actress%20of%20the%20Cannes%20entry%20Rehana%20Maryam%20Noor)%2C%20who%20fleshes%20out%20an%20intrepid%2C%20seductive%20undercover%20agent%20in%20a%20strikingly%20nuanced%20way%20and%20plays%20the%20character's%20indomitability%20off%20against%20her%20fragility%20to%20great%20effect%2C%20is%20a%20treat%20to%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAli%20Fazal%2C%20essaying%20the%20role%20of%20a%20man%20who%20allows%20himself%20to%20be%20manipulated%20fully%20mindful%20of%20what%20he%20is%20letting%20himself%20into%2C%20delivers%20a%20measured%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDirector%20Vishal%20Bhardwaj%20does%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20at%20full%20tilt%20in%20%3Cem%3EKhufiya%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20way%20he%20treats%20the%20intricacies%20of%20espionage%20and%20its%20human%20dimensions%20-%20he%20keeps%20it%20simple%20and%20direct%2C%20eschewing%20the%20gratuitously%20flashy%20-%20lends%20the%20film%20sustained%20solidity.%20Not%20to%20be%20missed.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696494180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fu0utrss_tabu-_625x300_05_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkhufiya-review-vishal-bhardwaj-keeps-gripping-spy-thriller-simple-and-direct-3-5-stars-4452079%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Khufiya%20Review%3A%20With%20the%20ever-reliable%20Tabu%20leading%20the%20way%2C%20the%20performances%20are%20right%20out%20of%20the%20top%20drawer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkhufiya-review-vishal-bhardwaj-keeps-gripping-spy-thriller-simple-and-direct-3-5-stars-4452079%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Raids%20on%2046%20Journalists%20Intimidation%2C%20Reminiscent%20of%20Emergency%3B%20Charges%20Against%20NewsClick%20Laughable%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05135024%2FKT-5-October.00_26_11_08.Still002.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20to%20discuss%20Tuesday%E2%80%99s%20sweeping%20raids%20against%2046%20journalists%20in%2050%20houses%20and%20offices%20carried%20out%20by%20over%20200%20policemen%2C%20former%20chief%20media%20advisor%20to%20Manmohan%20Singh%20when%20he%20was%20prime%20minister%2C%20Sanjaya%20Baru%2C%20has%20said%20this%20is%20%E2%80%9Cintimidation%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Ca%20fishing%20expedition%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Creminiscent%20of%20the%20Emergency%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Baru%2C%20who%20was%20earlier%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20said%20the%20scale%20of%20this%20operation%20is%20%E2%80%9Ca%20sign%20of%20incompetence%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20police.%20He%20said%20it%20is%20ridiculous%20to%20question%20journalists%20about%20whether%20they%20covered%20events%20such%20as%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests%2C%20the%20protests%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Act%20and%20the%20Delhi%20riots.%20Journalists%20are%20duty%20bound%20to%20cover%20such%20developments%20and%20the%20mere%20fact%20they%20have%20done%20so%20cannot%20by%20any%20leap%20of%20the%20imagination%20be%20deemed%20to%20be%20anti-national.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20specifically%20about%20the%20charges%20against%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20and%20Amit%20Chakravarty%20of%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Baru%20described%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Claughable%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThree%20specific%20sets%20of%20charges%20against%20the%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20journalists%20were%20discussed%20with%20Baru.%20They%20are%20the%20claim%20that%20they%20used%20Chinese%20money%20%E2%80%9Cto%20create%20disaffection%20amongst%20various%20sections%20of%20society%E2%80%9D%20including%20creating%20%E2%80%9Ca%20false%20narrative%20%E2%80%A6%20to%20discredit%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20contain%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic%E2%80%9D.%20Second%2C%20the%20police%20claim%20that%20%E2%80%9Csecret%20inputs%20revealed%20%E2%80%A6%20(Neville%20Roy%20Singham%20and%20Purkayastha)%20exchanged%20emails%20which%20expose%20their%20intent%20to%20show%20Kashmir%20and%20Arunachal%20is%20not%20part%20of%20India%20%E2%80%A6%20(thus)%20undermining%20the%20unity%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20India%E2%80%9D.%20The%20third%20charge%20against%20the%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20journalists%20is%20their%20friendship%20with%20Gautam%20Navlakha%20since%201991%20and%20the%20fact%20he%20is%20a%20shareholder%20of%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20since%20its%20inception%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBaru%20also%20said%20it%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Ca%20sad%20day%E2%80%9D%20that%20no%20editor%20of%20any%20major%20newspaper%20or%20major%20news%20channel%20was%20present%20at%20the%20protest%20held%20at%20the%20Press%20Club%20of%20India%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FsLnD7hqkarU%3Fsi%3D-sqDbzoSeYvLKfyZ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3