%20and%20caught%20Dr%20Shinde%20red-handed.%20He%20was%20prosecuted%20under%20provisions%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202012%2C%20a%20special%20court%20acquitted%20Dr%20Shinde%20of%20all%20charges%20which%20was%20challenged%20by%20the%20state%20in%20the%20high%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%2C%20however%2C%20found%20no%20merit%20in%20the%20state's%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20instant%20case%2C%20the%20allegation%20is%20acceptance%20of%20a%20bribe%20of%20Rs%20100%20in%20the%20year%202007.%20The%20amount%20appears%20to%20be%20too%20small%20in%20the%20year%202007%20and%20more%20so%2C%20in%20the%20year%202023%20when%20the%20appeal%20is%20being%20heard%20against%20the%20acquittal%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%20in%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20assuming%20that%20the%20appellant-complainant%20is%20able%20to%20prove%20the%20charges%20(although%2C%20I%20have%20already%20held%20that%20they%20have%20failed%20to%20prove%20the%20charges)%2C%20in%20my%20view%20after%20considering%20quantum%20at%20the%20relevant%20time%20this%20could%20be%20a%20fit%20case%20to%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20trivial%20matter%20to%20uphold%20the%20acquittal%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20relied%20on%20certain%20provisions%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%20that%20if%20the%20alleged%20bribe%20of%20gratification%20is%20trivial%2C%20then%20no%20inference%20of%20corruption%20may%20be%20drawn%20and%20the%20court%20may%20refuse%20to%20presume%20that%20the%20accused%20is%20corrupt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20dismissed%20the%20state%20government's%20appeal.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696493520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3