m%3EThe%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20said.%20The%20news%20report%20was%20based%20on%20leaked%20British%20intelligence%20that%20said%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20in%20Yellow%20Sea%20on%20August%2021.%20The%20submarine%20was%20identified%20as%20093-417%2C%20which%20was%20armed%20with%20torpedoes.%20China%20has%20denied%20the%20loss%20of%20any%20submarine%20in%20the%20region%2C%20but%20the%20news%20report%20has%20been%20making%20waves%20across%20the%20world.%20The%20captain%20and%2021%20officers%20are%20among%20the%20dead%2C%20the%20report%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%20to%20the%20Chinese%20submarine%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fchina-kills-own-sailors-with-trap-set-for-us-and-british-vessels-75wdfkc2p%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%C2%A0Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%2C%20the%20submarine%20was%20caught%20in%20a%20'chain%20and%20anchor%20obstacle'%2C%20which%20was%20laid%20there%20to%20trap%20the%20submarines%20of%20the%20US%20and%20allied%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20reportedly%20resulted%20in%20systems%20failure%20that%20required%20six%20hours%20of%20repair%20before%20the%20submarine%20could%20resurface.%20By%20then%2C%20the%20oxygen%20systems%20malfunctioned%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%2055%20crew%20members%20from%20hypoxia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20on-board%20oxygen%20system%20poisoned%20the%20crew%20after%20a%20catastrophic%20failure%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20British%20intelligence%20officials%20said%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EConcerns%20about%20water%20contamination%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20no%20independent%20confirmation%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinas-nuclear-submarine-suffers-catastrophic-failure-55-dead-report-4448320%5C%22%3Esuspected%20loss%20of%20the%20Chinese%20submarine%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20come%20to%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20experts%20have%20spoken%20about%20what%20this%20means%20for%20marine%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20incident%20has%20occurred%2C%20the%20global%20silence%20is%20perplexing.%20A%20nuclear%20submarine%20sinking%20should%20lead%20to%20global%20attention%20because%20a%20nuclear%20reactor%20leak%20due%20to%20damage%20can%20have%20serious%20consequences%2C%20including%20water%20contamination%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20submarine%20expert%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EEurAsian%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20fears%20that%20structural%20failure%20with%20the%20submarine%20reactors%20could%20cause%20a%20release%20of%20highly%20radioactive%20fission%20products%20and%20lead%20to%20%26quot%3Ba%20significant%20risk%20to%20life%20to%20those%20nearby%20and%20a%20public%20safety%20hazard%20to%20people%20in%20the%20big%20radius.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAll%20about%20Type-093attack%20submarines%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20submarines%20entered%20service%20in%20the%20last%2015%20years.%20The%20vessels%20are%20351-feet-long%20and%20are%20armed%20with%20torpedoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20six%20Type-093%20attack%20submarines%2C%20which%20have%20a%20displacement%20of%206%2C096%20tonnes.%20The%20nuclear-%20powered%20submarines%20are%20designed%20to%20be%20quieter%20than%20previous%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696492080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fu06bai88_china-nuclear-arsenal-china-submarine-reuters_625x300_29_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-nuclear-submarine-suffers-catastrophic-failure-what-we-know-4451948%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chinese%20nuclear%20submarine%20disaster%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%2055%20sailors.%20They%20died%20from%20hypoxia%20after%20oxygen%20systems%20malfunctioned.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchinese-nucle