those%20who%20were%20elected%20to%20power%20by%20raising%20the%20slogan%20of%20%26quot%3BIndia%20against%20corruption%26quot%3B%20have%20now%20been%20found%20steeped%20in%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Youth%20Affairs%20and%20Sports%20Minister%20arrived%20here%20to%20attend%20a%20couple%20of%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAAP's%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20Sanjay%20Singh%20was%20on%20Wednesday%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20New%20Delhi%20in%20connection%20with%20its%20money%20laundering%20probe%20linked%20to%20the%202021-22%20Delhi%20Excise%20policy%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20allegations%20against%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20after%20Singh's%20arrest%2C%20Mr%20Thakur%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20laughing%20at%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20ji%20and%20tension%20can%20be%20seen%20on%20his%20face.%20They%20are%20those%20people%20who%20came%20by%20raising%20the%20slogan%20of%20'India%20against%20corruption'%20and%20are%20now%20found%20steeped%20in%20corruption%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Punjab%2C%20it%20(AAP)%20got%20elected%20to%20power%20and%20within%20two%20months%2C%20the%20state%20health%20minister%20had%20to%20resign%20due%20to%20corruption%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKejriwal%20ji%20has%20no%20answer%20to%20the%20liquor%20scam%20that%20has%20brought%20shame%20to%20him.%20So%20far%2C%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20(of%20Delhi)%20and%20others%20have%20gone%20to%20jail%2C%20but%20the%20kingpin%20is%20still%20out.%20The%20probe%20is%20underway%20and%20the%20turn%20of%20the%20kingpin%20will%20also%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thakur%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20persons%20to%20whom%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20had%20distributed%20%26quot%3Bcertificates%20of%20honesty%26quot%3B%20are%20in%20jail%20since%20the%20last%20one%20year.%20Who%20gave%20him%20the%20right%20to%20distribute%20the%20certificates%2C%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EAgli%20kiski%20baari%20hai%2C%20ye%20media%20ke%20headline%20banne%20ki%20tayyari%20hai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(whose%20turn%20is%20next%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20media's%20headline)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Thakur%20also%20targeted%20the%20Congress%20governments%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20where%20the%20assembly%20elections%20are%20due%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20are%20the%20two%20states%20where%20officers%20close%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%20faced%20serious%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20and%20crores%20of%20rupees%20and%20gold%20were%20recovered%20from%20them.%20They%20(Chief%20Ministers)%20should%20have%20been%20resigned.%20But%20they%20haven't%20stepped%20down%20yet.%20Now%20people%20will%20oust%20them%20(in%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20caste%20survey%20done%20by%20the%20Bihar%20government%2C%20Mr%20Thakur%20mentioned%20that%20PM%20Modi%20has%20said%20his%20government%20is%20for%20the%20poor%2C%20down-%20trodden%20and%20those%20exploited.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20community%20is%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20we%20have%20to%20bring%20them%20out%20of%20poverty.%20In%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20of%20Modi%20ji's%20government%2C%2018.5%20crore%20people%20in%20the%20country%20have%20been%20pulled%20out%20of%20below%20poverty%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStatistics%20show%20how%20much%20works%20have%20been%20done%20for%20welfare%20of%20the%20poor%20in%20the%20country.%20When%20the%20Congress%20and%20its%20allies%20did%20not%20have%20an%20answer%20to%20it%2C%20they%20resorted%20to%20the%20caste%20issue%2C%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publ