trong%3ESquash%3A%201%20Medal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20won%20the%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%20mixed%20doubles%20event%20after%20Dipika%20Pallikal%20and%20Harinder%20Pal%20Singh%20Sandhu%20defeated%20the%20Malaysian%20pair.%20India%20are%20assured%20of%20another%20medal%20in%20squash%2C%20having%20reached%20the%20men's%20singles%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWrestling%3A%206%20Medals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFreestyle%20wrestling%20is%20where%20India%20are%20at%20their%20strongest%20in%20the%20sport.%20With%20Antim%20Panghal%2C%20Pooja%20Gehlot%20participating%2C%20India%20can%20hope%20for%202%20medals%20in%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20also%20have%20Kiran%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia%20participating%20in%20the%2065kg%20and%2076kg%20categories%20respectively%2C%20India%20can%20expect%20medals%20from%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDeepak%20Punia%20and%20Sumit%20also%20remain%20two%20top%20contenders%20in%20the%20men's%20freestyle%2086kg%20and%20125kg%20categories%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHockey%3A%202%20Medals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20men's%20team%20has%20entered%20the%20final%20and%20is%20assured%20of%20a%20medal.%C2%A0The%20women's%20team%20is%20also%20in%20the%20semi-finals%2C%20without%20losing%20a%20single%20contest.%20The%20side%20is%20expected%20to%20fetch%20at%20least%20a%20medal.%20Hopefully%2C%20the%20colour%20of%20those%20medals%20will%20be%20golden.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EArchery%3A%203%20medals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20compound%20events%2C%20India%20have%20been%20a%20formidable%20force%20in%20the%20Asian%20Games.%20Jyothi%20Surekha%20is%20expected%20to%20fetch%20India%20a%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%20individual%20final.%20Having%20reached%20the%20final%2C%20she%20is%20already%20assured%20of%20a%20medal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20men's%20compound%20gold%20medal%20match%2C%20India%20are%20assured%20of%20two%20medals%2C%20with%20Abhishek%20Verm