%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Carolina%20Reaper%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20spiciest%20chilli%20in%20the%20world.%20It%20has%20an%20average%20of%201.64%20million%20Scoville%20Heat%20Units%20(SHU)%2C%20which%20measures%20the%20pungency%20of%20chilli%20peppers%20and%20other%20items.%20It's%20said%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bhundreds%20of%20times%20hotter%20than%20a%20jalapeno%20pepper%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guinnessworldrecords.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F9%2Fspeed-eater-scoffs-50-carolina-reaper-chillies-in-record-time-758909%5C%22%3EGuinness%20World%20Records%3C%2Fa%3E%20(GWR).%20Recently%2C%20a%20Canadian%20man%20broke%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffood%2Fwatch-this-indian-man-made-a-world-record-by-drinking-capri-sun-in-less-than-10-seconds-4417459%5C%22%3Eworld%20record%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20eating%2050%20of%20these%20chillies%20in%20the%20fastest%20time.%20Speed%20eater%20Mike%20Jack%20(Canada)%20managed%20this%20feat%20in%206%20minutes%20and%2049.2%20seconds.%20That's%20not%20all%3A%20after%20devouring%20the%2050%20peppers%2C%20he%20ate%2085%20more!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20data-ved%3D%5C%222ahUKEwjd_pa9jNyBAxXN3TgGHVMXB1IQxfQBKAB6BAgHEAE%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffood%2Fonion-weighing-more-than-bowling-ball-breaks-world-record-details-inside-4438144%5C%22%20ping%3D%5C%22%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26amp%3Bsource%3Dweb%26amp%3Brct%3Dj%26amp%3Bopi%3D89978449%26amp%3Burl%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffood%2Fonion-weighing-more-than-bowling-ball-breaks-world-record-details-inside-4438144%26amp%3Bved%3D2ahUKEwjd_pa9jNyBAxXN3TgGHVMXB1IQxfQBKAB6BAgHEAE%5C%22%3EOnion%20Weighing%20More%20Than%20Bowling%20Ball%20Breaks%20World%20Record%20-%20Details%20Inside%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGWR%20has%20also%20shared%20Jack's%20words%20about%20his%20experience%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20first%20pepper%20is%20the%20worst.%20The%20initial%20shock%20of%20spiciness%20is%20intense.%20The%20second%20one%20doesn't%20seem%20as%20bad%2C%20but%20each%20one%20after%20that%20gets%20hotter%20and%20hotter%20as%20the%20peppers%20touch%20new%20places%20in%20your%20mouth.%26quot%3B%20But%20the%20extreme%20discomfort%20brought%20on%20by%20the%20chillies%20doesn't%20just%20affect%20his%20mouth%20-%20it%20also%20wreaks%20havoc%20with%20his%20stomach.%20%26quot%3BI%20get%20bad%20cramps.%20It%20feels%20like%20someone%20is%20squeezing%20and%20twisting%20my%20guts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20GWR.%20%26quot%3BYour%20mind%20is%20telling%20you%20to%20stop%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20convince%20yourself%20to%20keep%20pushing%20through.%26quot%3B%20The%20site%20also%20revealed%20that%20Mike%20has%20worked%20to%20build%20up%20a%20%26quot%3Btolerance%20to%20spiciness%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20past%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWatch%20the%20video%20of%20Mike%20setting%20the%20record%20below%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENew%20record%3A%20Fastest%20time%20to%20eat%2050%20carolina%20reaper%20chilli%20peppers%20-%206%20minutes%20and%2049.20%20seconds%20by%20Mike%20Jack%20%F0%9F%87%A8%F0%9F%87%A6%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20He%20eventually%20went%20on%20to%20eat%20135%20peppers%20in%20this%20one%20sitting%20%F0%9F%A4%AF%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fb5OxTBtbjd%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fb5OxTBtbjd%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20%23GWR2024%20OUT%20NOW%20(%40GWR)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FGWR%2Fstatus%2F1706615782761799881%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EMike%20also%20holds%20the%20world%20record%20for%20the%20fastest%20time%20to%20drink%20a%20bottle%20of%20hot%20sauce%20(8.56%20seconds)%20and%20the%20fastest%20time%20to%20drink%20one%20litre%20of%20tomato%20sauce%20(1%20minute%205.56%20seconds)%20-%20both%20of%20which%20he%20achieved%20in%20August%20