114331%2F33F81A3F-BCF6-4D05-975C-264958F029F4_1_105_c.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Silence%20engulfed%20the%20audience%20when%20%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Wire%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20Arfa%20Khanum%20Sherwani%20told%20them%20that%20the%20biggest%20producer%2C%20director%20and%20actors%20of%20hate%20as%20well%20as%20violence%20in%20the%20country%20is%20the%20Indian%20government%20itself.%20The%20silence%20made%20Arfa%20ask%20them%20if%20they%20felt%20that%20she%20was%20exaggerating.%20She%20then%20moved%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20evidence%20to%20support%20it.%20As%20a%20journalist%2C%20this%20is%20my%20work%20to%20have%20facts%20and%20figures%20to%20support%20my%20statement.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi-based%20journalist%20was%20speaking%20to%20a%20jam-packed%20audience%20at%20the%20West%20Bengal%20Muslim%20Majlis-e-Mushawarat%E2%80%99s%20(WBMEM)%20symposium%20%E2%80%98Violence%20Free%20India%3A%20The%20Way%20Forward%E2%80%99%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20Sunday%20(October%201).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20journalist%20further%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20report%20by%20Hindutva%20Watch%20that%20in%20the%20first%20six%20months%20of%202023%2C%20there%20were%20255%20hate%20speech%20cases%20that%20took%20place%20in%20India.%20And%2080%25%20of%20this%20happened%20in%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-ruled%20states.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArfa%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20organisation%20is%20based%20in%20Washington%20DC%20and%20does%20not%20report%20from%20the%20ground.%20So%2C%20they%20have%20mentioned%20only%20documented%20incidents.%20This%20means%20there%20could%20be%20more%20cases.%20The%20government%20has%20stopped%20collecting%20such%20data%20in%202017%20itself.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20mentioned%20the%20Washington%20Post%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fworld%2F2023%2F09%2F26%2Fhindu-nationalist-social-media-hate-campaign%2F%5C%22%3Einvestigative%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20said%20that%20during%20the%20Karnataka%20election%2C%20hate%20was%20a%20part%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20election%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20least%201.5%20lakh%20people%20were%20employed%20to%20spread%20hate%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenewsroom.in%2Fharidwar-hate-speech-dharam-sansad-minorities%2F%5C%22%3Eagainst%3C%2Fa%3E%20Muslims%20and%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20were%20told%20that%20if%20they%20wanted%20to%20be%20saved%2C%20they%20should%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20government%20and%20prime%20minister%20has%20their%20policies%20and%20agendas%20to%20work%20for.%20%5BBut%5D%20this%20government%20only%20has%20an%20agenda%20to%20spread%20hate%20and%20violence%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnuh-riots-fact-finding-team-persecution-of-muslims%5C%22%3ENuh%20Riots%20Correspond%20to%20Larger%20Persecution%20of%20Region%E2%80%99s%20Muslims%3A%20Fact-Finding%20Team%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJaishankar%20Gupta%2C%20senior%20journalist%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Press%20Council%20of%20India%2C%20claimed%20that%20he%20has%20not%20seen%20a%20%E2%80%98foolish%E2%80%99%20prime%20minister%20like%20Modi.%20He%20cited%20many%20statements%20from%20Modi%20to%20validate%20his%20claim.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20Nalanda%20and%20Takshashila%20universities%20in%20Bihar.%20Takshshila%20is%20in%20Pakistan.%20In%20the%20same%20event%20he%20said%2C%20Sikandar%20along%20with%20his%20Deen-e-Ilahi%20(religion)%20drowned%20here%20only%20in%20Ganga.%20But%20Sikandar%20never%20came%20to%20this%20part.%20And%20Deen-e-Ilahi%20was%20founded%20by%20Akbar%2C%20not%20Sikandar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20does%20not%20know%20much%20about%20his%20political%20father%20either.%20He%20said%20that%20Shyama%20Prasad%20Mukherjee%20used%20to%20go%20to%20London%20and%20hold%20discussions%20with%20Vivekanand.%20A%20whole%20book%20can%20be%20written%20on%20his%20lies.%20He%20even%20said%20that%20Guru%20Gorakhnath%2C%20Kabir%20and%20Gurunanak%20used%20to%20brainstorm.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20200-year%20of%20difference%20in%20their%20existence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20(Modi)%20even%20lied%20inside%20the%20parliament.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20Shimla%20agreement%20was%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20Benazir%20Bhutto.%20But%20no%20opposition%20leader%20raised%20the%20fact%20that%20Bhutto%20was%20only%2016%20years%20old%20then.%20Recently%2C%20he%20said%20that%20AIIMS%20is%20functional%20in%20Darbhanga%2C%20while%20it%20is%20non-existent%20till%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInsecure%20politicians%20promote%20violence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMagsaysay%20Award%20winner%20Sandeep%20Pandey%20pointed%20out%20that%20while%20the%20voting%20pattern%20is%20different%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20both%20Hindu-Muslim%20people%20are%20co-existing%20in%20the%20state.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20Gujarat%2C%20cities%20like%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20are%20living%20in%20different%20localities.%20In%20Hindu%20areas%2C%20you%20will%20not%20meet%20Muslim%20residents%20and%20in%20Muslim%20areas%2C%20Hindus%20do%20not%20reside.%20But%20the%20situation%20in%20UP%20is%20not%20like%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Ashok%20Ganguly%20claimed%20that%20most%20political%20leaders%20are%20insecure%20so%20they%20promote%20violence.%20They%20feel%20that%20they%20will%20lose%20the%20next%20election%20if%20they%20do%20not%20promote%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fquestioned-on-minorities-jaishankar-says-show-me-discrimination-the-facts-he-can-see%5C%22%3EQuestioned%20on%20Minorities%2C%20Jaishankar%20Says%20%E2%80%98Show%20Me%20Discrimination%E2%80%99.%20The%20Facts%20He%20Can%20See.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20retired%20judge%20also%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20has%20been%20violence%20done%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20well%20in%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20case.%20When%20ASI%20in%20its%20report%20had%20said%20that%20there%20was%20no%20temple%20structure%20inside%20Babri%20Mosque%2C%20then%20how%20can%20they%20give%20a%20decision%20in%20favour%20of%20Hindus%3F%20By%20what%20logic%20was%20it%20done%3F%20This%20is%20promoting%20violence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20Congress%20leader%20Tarique%20Anwar%20also%20addressed%20the%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20event%2C%20a%20poem%20was%20recited%20by%20the%20Muslim%20people%20of%20Manipur%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Ffive-months-into-manipur-conflict-justice-evades-those-who-lost-their-loved-ones%5C%22%3Efive-month%20long%20ethnic%20cleansing%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20general%20secretary%20of%20WBMEM%2C%20Manzar%20Jameel%20explained%20to%20the%20audience%20the%20need%20for%20having%20chosen%20the%20topic%20for%20the%20symposium.%20He%20cited%20many%20recent%20incidents%20of%20violence%20in%20which%20minority%20communities%20like%20Dalits%20and%20Adivasis%20faced%20attacks%20and%20it%20is%20increasing%20day%20by%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenewsroom.in%2Fviolence-free-india-politics-of-hate-muslim%2F%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenewsroom.in%2F%5C%22%3EeNewsroom%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696487867000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F12114331%2F33F81A3F-BCF6-4D05-975C-264958F029F4_1_105_c.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-state-is-the-biggest-producer-of-hate-and-violence-in-india-arfa-khanum-sherwani%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Speaking%20at%20West%20Bengal%20Muslim%20Majlis