0Melbourne.%20The%20Grand%20Final%20has%20just%20finished%2C%20his%20team%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20there%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think.%20Welcome%20Gideon%2C%20great%20to%20have%20you%20here%20at%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EOut%20of%20the%20Park%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20You%20are%20an%20opener%20and%20like%20Sehwag%2C%20we%20think%20you%E2%80%99re%20gonna%20play%20our%20shots%20today.%20So%2C%20so%20good%20to%20have%20you%20here.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EGideon%20Haigh%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20My%20club%20mates%20would%20laugh%20at%20me%20being%20associated%20with%20anything%20called%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EOut%20of%20the%20Park%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20because%20over%20the%20weekend%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20be%20playing%20my%20350th%20game%20in%20the%20club%20and%20I%20think%20I%E2%80%99ve%20probably%20hit%20about%2010%20sixes%20in%20all%20that%20time.%20But%20the%20great%20thing%20is%20I%20remember%20all%20of%20them!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESU%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Gideon%2C%20do%20you%20know%20that%20V.V.S.%20Laxman%20has%20hit%20literally%20under%20three%20or%20four%20sixes%20in%20his%20Test%20career%20so%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20kind%20of%20quality%20that%20you%E2%80%99re%20matching%20up%20with!%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EGH%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Bradman%20only%20hit%20six%20and%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20hit%20a%20six%20until%20the%20Bodyline%20series%20which%20was%20actually%20a%20sign%20that%20his%20game%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20in%20the%20best%20shape%2C%20that%20he%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20geared%20to%20hitting%20sixes%20and%20nor%20am%20I.%20That%E2%80%99s%20probably%20the%20%3Cem%3Eonly%3C%2Fem%3E%20thing%20that%20I%20have%20in%20common%20with%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F3fdrQrjAO4w%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22World%20Cup%20Cricket%20202