ered%20by%20cow%20vigilantes%20%E2%80%93%20interested%20more%20in%20extortion%20rather%20than%20the%20protection%20of%20cows%20%E2%80%93%20ever%20since%20the%20Haryana%20government%20passed%20the%20Cow%20Promotion%20and%20Protection%20Act%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20cow%20vigilantes%2C%20who%20describe%20themselves%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Egau%20rakshaks%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20have%20sprung%20up%20since%20the%20election%20of%20the%20BJP%20with%20an%20absolute%20majority%20at%20the%20Centre%20in%202014%2C%20as%20they%20enjoy%20impunity%20with%20the%20tacit%20patronage%20of%20those%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ever-increasing%20and%20exorbitant%20extortion%20demands%20by%20the%20cow%20vigilante%20networks%20have%20made%20it%20nearly%20impossible%20for%20the%20Meo%20Muslim%20agriculturists%20to%20pursue%20the%20only%20livelihood%20available%20to%20them%20%E2%80%93%20agriculture%20and%20dairy%20farming%20with%20diminishing%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20communal%20riots%20in%20Nuh%20that%20took%20place%20on%2031st%20July%202023%20is%20intricately%20linked%20with%20the%20systematic%20and%20blatant%20targeting%20of%20the%20Muslims%20in%20the%20region%20with%20no%20prospect%20of%20justice%20from%20the%20state.%20The%20residents%20have%20been%20aghast%20and%20resentful%20about%20how%20easily%20Muslim%20youth%20are%20kidnapped%20or%20abducted%20and%20murdered%20with%20the%20state%20doing%20little%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20culprits%20are%20brought%20to%20justice%2C%E2%80%9D%20states%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EIn%20Photos%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fin-photos-from-vehicles-to-a-police-station-nuh-looks-deserted-burnt-after-violence%5C%22%3EFrom%20Vehicles%20to%20a%20Police%20Station%2C%20Nuh%20Looks%20Deserted%2C%20Burnt%20After%20Violence%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20CSSS%E2%80%99s%20report%20cites%20the%20instance%20of%20Haji%20Jamat%20Ali%2C%20a%20man%20whose%20cattle%20wealth%20of%2056%20cows%2C%20kept%20in%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20field%20in%20Bai%20Kheda%20in%20Gurugram%20district%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsclick.in%2Fharyana-loot-name-cow-protection-cant-muslims-rear-cows%5C%22%3Ewas%20allegedly%20seized%20and%20taken%20away%20by%20vigilante%20youth%3C%2Fa%3E%20wearing%20saffron%20scarves%20and%20shouting%20communal%20slogans%20on%20June%2030.%20Ali%E2%80%99s%20only%20livelihood%20was%20dairy%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmuslimmirror.com%2Feng%2Fanatomy-of-violence-in-the-hithero-peaceful-nuh-a-fact-finding-report%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20states%20that%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20was%20booked%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20snatching%20the%20cattle%3B%20however%2C%20there%20are%20little%20prospects%20of%20proper%20and%20effective%20prosecution%20of%20the%20offenders%2C%20who%2C%20if%20Ali%E2%80%99s%20allegations%20are%20true%2C%20have%20committed%20dacoity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20that%20there%20were%20six%20other%20instances%20in%20which%20seven%20people%20were%20murdered%20by%20cow%20vigilantes%20from%20April%202017%20to%20February%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20the%20report%20says%20were%20killed%20by%20vigilantes%20are%20Pehlu%20Khan%3B%20Umar%20Mohammad%20from%20Ghatmika%20village%3B%20Rakbar%20Khan%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Kolgaon%3B%20Asif%20Khan%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Kher%20Khalilpur%20village%3B%20Waris%2C%20aged%2022%20years%3B%20and%20the%20last%20two%20murdered%20were%20Nasir%20and%20Junaid%20from%20Ghatmika%20village%2C%20who%20were%20abducted%20from%20Bharatpur%2C%20beaten%20to%20death%20and%20later%20burnt%20in%20their%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMonu%20Manesar%2C%20who%20is%20accused%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20Nasir%20and%20Junaid%E2%80%99s%20abduction%20and%20murder%20on%20February%2016%2C%202023%2C%20and%20who%20Waris%E2%80%99%20family%20said%20was%20behind%20his%20death%2C%20was%20still%20moving%20about%20freely%20on%20July%2031%2C%202023%2C%20when%20the%20riots%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20those%20murdered%20by%20the%20vigilantes%20were%20done%20to%20death%20brutally%20%E2%80%93%20Asif%20Khan%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2021%2F05%2F29%2Fmurder-or-mob-lynching-why-was-asif-khan-killed-in-nuh%5C%22%3Ewas%20allegedly%20stabbed%20in%20the%20eyes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20bones%20broken.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20other%20instances%2C%20the%20vigilantes%2C%20without%20any%20fear%20of%20the%20law%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.co.uk%2Farticle%2Findia-youtube-vigilante-monu-manesar-murder%5C%22%3Emade%20videos%20of%20their%20brutality%20and%20uploaded%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20their%20social%20media%20sites.%20The%20chilling%20videos%20were%20uploaded%20to%20instil%20fear%20in%20the%20minority%20community%20so%20that%20they%20could%20run%20their%20extortion%20racket.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20resulted%20in%20growing%20anger%20against%20the%20state%20and%20the%20police%20among%20the%20minority%20community%2C%20and%20a%20feeling%20of%20helplessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhow-violent-cow-vigilantism-made-monu-manesar-an-icon%5C%22%3EHow%20Violent%20Cow%20Vigilantism%20Made%20Monu%20Manesar%20an%20Icon%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Meo%20Muslim%20community%20fought%20the%20Mughals%20and%20opposed%20%5Bthe%5D%20partition%20of%20the%20country%2C%20and%20Mewat%20was%20called%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBharat%20ki%20reed%20ki%20haddi%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20%5BHindi%20for%20%E2%80%98backbone%20of%20India%E2%80%99%5D%20by%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%9D%2C%20said%20Dabhade.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBeing%20an%20agricultural%20community%2C%20Meo%20Muslims%20are%20well-integrated%20into%20Mewat%E2%80%99s%20local%20customs%20and%20cultural%20traditions%2C%20and%20are%20hardly%20distinguishable%20from%20other%20residents%20of%20the%20region.%20They%20follow%20Lal%20Khan%20Meo%2C%20popularly%20known%20as%20Baba%20Laldas%20to%20the%20Meo%20Muslims%2C%20who%20preached%20cow-worship%2C%20vegetarianism%20and%20chanting%20Lord%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20name%2C%20states%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9C%5Bt%5Dhere%20are%20many%20oral%20epics%20in%20this%20region%20where%20Muslim%20%3Ci%3Ejogis%3C%2Fi%3E%20have%20popularised%20epics%20like%20Gopichand%2C%20Bhartrihari%20and%20%3Ci%3EPandavon%20ka%20Kada%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20indicating%20their%20affinity%20with%20Hindu%20religious%20traditions%20%E2%80%A6%20their%20folklore%2C%20which%20attributes%20their%20%E2%80%A6%20origin%20to%20Arjuna%2C%20Krishna%20and%20Rama%3B%20they%20celebrate%20Hindu%20festivals%20like%20Holi%20and%20Dussehra%3B%20their%20marriage%20customs%20combine%20%3Cem%3Enikah%3C%2Fem%3E%20with%20Hindu%20ceremonies%3B%20their%20mixed%20names%20such%20as%20Fateh%20Singh%20%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20states%20that%20while%20there%20was%20a%20green%20revolution%20and%20networks%20of%20canal%20irrigation%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%2C%20the%20development%20of%20the%20Mewat%20region%20%E2%80%93%20which%20remained%20rainfed%20with%20scant%20rainfall%20%E2%80%93%20was%20ignored.%20The%20Muslim%20youth%20have%20no%20prospect%20of%20non-agricultural%20livelihoods%2C%20as%20there%20are%20no%20higher%20educational%20institutions%20or%20industrial%20units%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20Meo%20Muslims%20used%20to%20sell%20biryani%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20famous%20%E2%80%93%20along%20the%20highway.%20However%2C%20under%20pressure%20from%20vigilantes%20or%20out%20of%20their%20own%20prejudice%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F816317%2Fwhy-popular-biryani-joints-in-haryanas-mewat-district-have-shut-shop-this-eid%5C%22%3Epolice%20seized%20their%20cooking%20equipment%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20vessels%20and%20biryani%2C%20accused%20them%20of%20using%20beef%20and%20sent%20their%20biryani%20for%20testing%20in%20laboratories.%20The%20community%20had%20to%20abandon%20their%20business%20due%20to%20the%20harassment%20and%20seizures%2C%20which%20led%20to%20heavy%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FvZnhfq2nQls%3Fsi%3DZmfX_8jvAR2tWH3J%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20Muslim%20youth%20took%20to%20cyber%20fraud.%20However%2C%20this%20time%20the%20police%20was%20proactive%20in%20arresting%20them%20%E2%80%93%20and%20rightly%20so%20%E2%80%93%20unlike%20the%20treatment%20given%20to%20crimes%20committed%20by%20cow%20vigilantes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20pent-up%20feeling%20of%20frustration%20was%20further%20aggravated%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fharyana-violence-mewat-hate-and-provocative-videos%5C%22%3EBittu%20Bajrangi%20and%20Monu%20Manesar%20posted%20offensive%20and%20provocative%20videos%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20social%20media%20announcing%20their%20arrival%20on%20July%2031%20to%20Nuh%20along%20with%20the%20Braj%20Mandal%20%3Cem%3Ejalabhishek%20yatr%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20led%20by%20the%20Vishva%20Hindu%20Parishad%20(VHP).%20They%20challenged%20the%20%E2%80%98manhood%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20Muslim%20community%20to%20receive%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20Muslim%20youth%20fell%20into%20the%20trap%20and%20were%20prepared%20to%20meet%20the%20situation%20should%20they%20spot%20either%20of%20them.%20In%20their%20anxiety%2C%20the%20Muslim%20youth%20who%20were%20prepared%20to%20receive%20the%20two%20miscreants%20spotted%20a%20white%20car%20and%20believed%20that%20Monu%20Manesar%20was%20in%20the%20car%2C%20the%20report%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20Muslim%20boy%20was%20knocked%20down%20as%20the%20car%20reversed%20and%20sped%20away.%20The%20car%20was%20chased%20and%20stopped%2C%20and%20Bittu%20Bajrangi%20was%20pulled%20out%2C%20states%20the%20report.%20This%20led%20to%20the%20attack%20by%20a%20group%20of%20Muslim%20youth%20and%20the%20consequent%20alleged%20firing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fnews%2Fcrime%2Fkin-remember-home-guard-officer-neeraj-lal-killed-in-nuh-haryana-riots-violence%23read-more%5C%22%3ETwo%20home%20guards%20and%20three%20other%20Hindus%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20violence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20quotes%20eyewitness%20stating%20that%20provocative%20slogans%20targeting%20the%20Muslim%20community%20were%20being%20shouted%2C%20including%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMulle%20kate%20jayenge%2C%20Ram%20ran%20chillayenge%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(%E2%80%98As%20Muslims%20will%20be%20slaughtered%2C%20they%20will%20chant%20the%20name%20of%20Lord%20Ram%E2%80%99).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20participants%20in%20the%20procession%20were%20carrying%20arms.%20The%20participants%20attacked%20and%20destroyed%20property%20and%20businesses%20belonging%20to%20the%20Muslims%20in%20Nuh%20as%20well%2C%20a%20fact%20that%20has%20been%20largely%20ignored%20by%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnuh-violence-rpf-constables-murder-new-phase-anti-muslim-hate%5C%22%3ENuh%20Violence%20and%20RPF%20Constable%E2%80%99s%20Murder%20Spree%20Reveal%20a%20New%20Phase%20of%20Anti-Muslim%20Hate%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESandhya%20Mhatre%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20fact-finding%20team%20who%20was%20in%20Nuh%20on%20August%2028%20%E2%80%93%20when%20the%20VHP%20had%20threatened%20to%20take%20out%20the%20jalabhishek%20yatra%20once%20again%20%E2%80%93%20told%20this%20author%20that%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20near%20inaction%20and%20failure%20of%20the%20police%20on%20July%2031%20in%20preventing%20and%20controlling%20the%20riots%2C%20the%20team%20on%20August%2028%20witnessed%20heavy%20police%20deployment%20and%20checkpoints%20in%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20Nuh%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolice%20were%20checking%20every%20vehicle%20and%20every%20stranger%20to%20ensure%20that%20outsiders%20did%20not%20enter%20the%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20meant%20that%20the%20Haryana%20police%20were%20capable%20of%20preventing%20the%20riot%20on%20July%2031%20if%20they%20had%20possessed%20the%20same%20determination.%20However%2C%20on%20that%20day%2C%20police%20presence%20was%20scant%20and%20they%20utterly%20failed%20in%20discharging%20their%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20riots%2C%20police%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20arresting%20a%20large%20number%20of%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20youths.%20They%20could%20see%20only%20women%2C%20children%20and%20old%20people%20in%20their%20homes%20%E2%80%93%20young%20and%20able-bodied%20men%20had%20run%20away%20to%20escape%20being%20falsely%20and%20indiscriminately%20accused%20of%20rioting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20were%20egged%20on%20to%20act%20indiscriminately%20by%20public%20statements%20given%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20home%20minister%20of%20Haryana%20to%20teach%20rioters%20a%20lesson.%20The%20vindictive%20action%20included%20the%20demolition%20of%20more%20than%20750%20homes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F2023%2F08%2F19%2Fnuh-750-homes-shops-demolished-locals-blame-govt-false-media-narrative%5C%22%3Emost%20of%20which%20reportedly%20belonged%20to%20Muslims%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20although%20some%20members%20of%20the%20jalabhishek%20procession%20were%20also%20involved%20in%20rioting.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20demanded%20an%20impartial%20probe%20into%20the%20violence%20by%20a%20special%20investigation%20team%20under%20judicial%20supervision%2C%20bringing%20to%20justice%20all%20rioters%20irrespective%20of%20their%20religion%2C%20and%20the%20release%20of%20those%20youth%20against%20whom%20there%20is%20no%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20further%20demanded%20strict%20action%20against%20cow%20vigilantes%20to%20ensure%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20the%20dismantling%20of%20their%20extortionist%20network.%20The%20report%20also%20demanded%20reparations%20to%20the%20survivors%20of%20the%20riots%2C%20making%20good%20their%20losses%20and%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20properties%20that%20were%20demolished%20by%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIrfan%20Engineer%20is%20Director%2C%20Centre%20for%20Study%20of%20Society%20and%20Secularism.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1696478166000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F02105441%2F5.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnuh-riots-fact-finding-team-persecution-of-muslims%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20fact-finding%20team%20constituted%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20Study%20of%20Society%20and%20Secularism%20found%20that%20Nuh's%20residents%20were%20resentful%20about%20how%20easily%20its%20Muslim%20youth%20were%20abducted%20or%20killed%20while%20the%20culprits%20enjoyed%20impunity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnuh-riots-fact-finding-team-persecution-of-muslims%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20What%20Happens%20When%20a%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20Doubles%20as%20a%20'Massive%20Display%20of%20Egocentricity'%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F05092049%2FUntitled-design-5.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVeteran%20sports%20writer%20Sharda%20Ugra%20hits%20it%20%E2%80%98Out%20of%20the%20Park%E2%80%99%20with%20Gideon%20Haigh%20in%20the%20inaugural%20episode%20of%20her%20show%20on%20all%20things%20cricket%20World%20Cup%2C%20where%20they%20talk%20about%20the%20sport%2C%20the%20fanfare%2C%20the%20festival%20and%20the%20politics%20implicit%20in%20all%20of%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allo