nd%20would%20either%20have%20to%20walk%20or%20take%20a%20rickshaw%20to%20reach%20us.%20This%20also%20makes%20it%20difficult%20for%20families%20to%20visit%20us%20at%20night%20after%20other%20shops%20shut.%20So%2C%20I%20worked%20on%20opening%20outlets%20that%20were%20easily%20accessible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPriced%20between%20Rs%2080%20and%20Rs%20250%2C%20today%2C%20at%20least%201%2C000%20customers%20relish%20Kuremal%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Ekulfi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eevery%20day.%20Commenting%20on%20their%20note-worthy%20customers%2C%20Vishal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20invited%20to%20serve%20%3Cem%3Ekulfi%3C%2Fem%3Es%20to%20guests%20in%20parties%20hosted%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20Ambanis%2C%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20Even%20today%2C%20our%20%3Cem%3Ekulfi%3C%2Fem%3Es%20are%20appreciated%20at%20the%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVishal%20says%20what%20the%20customers%20love%20the%20most%20is%20the%20stuffed%20fruit%20%3Cem%3Ekulfi%3C%2Fem%3Es.%20His%20father%20introduced%20stuffed%20%3Cem%3Ekulfi%3C%2Fem%3Es%20to%20their%20eatery%20in%201980.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCo_pG8dvREV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCo_pG8dvREV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3