on%20till%20my%20last%20breath%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhan%2C%20who%20still%20works%20as%20a%20daily%20wager%20to%20eke%20out%20his%20living%2C%20has%20dedicated%20two%20days%20a%20week%20to%20nurturing%20these%20trees.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20climate%20is%20very%20hot%2C%20these%20%3Cem%3Echinars%20%3C%2Fem%3Erequire%20to%20be%20watered%20periodically.%20So%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20work%20for%20two%20days%20a%20week%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20I%20spend%20my%20entire%20day%20watering%20them.%20Though%20I%20am%20poor%20and%20work%20as%20a%20labourer%2C%20I%20nurture%20these%20trees%20like%20my%20own%20kids%3B%20they%20are%20like%20my%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKhan%20has%20not%20married%20and%20lives%20with%20his%20mother%20and%20brothers.%20He%20has%20inspired%20his%20family%20and%20others%20to%20look%20after%20the%20%3Cem%3Echinars%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20%3Cem%3Echinars%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Khan%20has%20now%20extended%20his%20mission%20by%20planting%20%3Cem%3Edeodar%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20other%20pine%20trees%20in%20the%20forests.%20He%20can%20expertly%20handle%20this%20task%20now%20after%20updating%20himself%20about%20it.%20He%20continues%20to%20work%20in%20plantation%20drives%20and%20hopes%20that%20others%20will%20recognise%20the%20need%20for%20immediate%20afforestation%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20many%20aren%E2%80%99t%20much%20interested%20in%20this%20type%20of%20social%20work%20in%20my%20area%2C%20there%20are%20still%20some%20who%20visit%20and%20help%20me%20out.%20I%20hope%20someday%2C%20everyone%20realises%20the%20need%20for%20a%20green%20and%20clean%20environment%20and%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F124279%2Fpics-first-snows-transform-kashmir-mystical-wonderland-look%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMother%20Nature%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20conserved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E(%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1695994405000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D331243%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20daily%20wager%20turned%20'Father%20of%20Chinars'%2C%20Abdul%20Ahad%20Khan's%20mission%20to%20protect%20Kashmir%20Valley's%20iconic%20tree%20started%20in%20Hatmullah%2015%20years%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Firdous%20Hassan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20The%20Startup%20Creating%20Luxury%20Fashion%20From%20Waste%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERibhav%20Kapur%2C%20the%2038-year-old%20founder%20of%20Econock%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Delhi-based%20luxury%20brand%20which%20makes%20sustainable%20accessories%20%E2%80%94%20has%20always%20been%20inclined%20towards%20eclectic%20yet%20functional%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20training%20in%20fashion%20technology%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273270%2Fkhadi-solar-loom-charkha-nift-graduate-helps-women-earn-more%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Institute%20of%20Fashion%20Technology%20(NIFT)%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Mumbai%20equipped%20him%20to%20deliver%20efficient%20outcomes.%20For%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20this%20training%20came%20in%20handy%20in%20the%20world%20of%20%E2%80%98high%20fashion%E2%80%99%20working%20under%20renowned%20designer%20Manish%20Arora.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEverything%2C%20however%2C%20changed%20for%20Ribhav%20in%202017%20when%20he%20was%20working%20on%20a%20collaborative%20project%20between%20Manish%20Arora%20and%20Swarovski%2C%20the%20legacy%20Austrian%20jewellery%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Ribhav%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20do%20window%20installations%20for%20Swarovski%20using%20their%20crystals%20and%20beads.%20Due%20to%20unforeseen%20reasons%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20beads%20and%20crystals%20which%20were%20to%20be%20shipped%20by%20Swarovski%20got%20stuck%20in%20transit.%20We%20had%20to%20improvise%20to%20meet%20the%20deadline%20for%20the%20installations.%20So%2C%20we%20contacted%20Swarovski%20and%20got%20to%20know%20about%20the%20crystal%20dust%20(a%20byproduct%20of%20making%20crystals)%20which%20was%20available%20in%20various%20colours%20and%20sizes%20as%20well.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20made%20the%20installations%20using%20some%20beads%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20crystal%20dust%20from%20Swarovski%20besides%20old%20materials%20and%20unused%20fabrics%20in-house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHaving%20led%20operations%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F269112%2Fshillong-designer-fine-ryndia-silk-eco-friendly-fabric-daniel-syiem-ethnic-fashion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emajor%20designer%20%3C%2Fa%3Elabel%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20Ribhav%20understood%20that%20optimising%20time%20and%20design%20quality%20were%20the%20primary%20production%20parameters.%20A%20clear%20focus%20on%20design%2C%20quality%2C%20cost%20and%20time%20left%20little%20room%20to%20optimise%20wastage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20only%20this%20Swarovski%20project%20which%20required%20us%20to%20work%20with%20limited%20resources%2C%20for%20whom%20we%20curated%20an%20installation.%20This%20was%20truly%20a%20eureka%20moment%20for%20me.%20It%20gave%20me%20a%20perspective%20of%20how%20limited%20resources%20can%20empower%20creative%20designing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20curiosity%20led%20him%20away%20from%20the%20world%20of%20traditional%20high%20fashion%20to%20pursue%20a%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree%20in%20sustainability%20from%20Malm%C3%B6%20University%20in%20Sweden%2C%20where%20he%20was%20exposed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cnewfound%20knowledge%20on%20sustainable%20business%20practices%2C%20the%20circular%20economy%2C%20and%20upcycling%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCombining%20my%20love%20for%20adventure%20and%20innovation%2C%20I%20set%20out%20to%20build%20my%20dream%20project%20%E2%80%94%20Econock%2C%20a%20brand%20that%20creates%20luxurious%20accessories%20through%20upcycling%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERibhav%E2%80%99s%20dream%20project%20began%20with%20upcycling%20scrap%20leather%20to%20make%20accessories.%20Established%20in%202020%2C%20Econock%20makes%20a%20range%20of%20accessories%20comprising%20bags%2C%20satchels%2C%20wallets%2C%20bracelets%2C%20phone%20slings%20and%20passport%20cases%2C%20among%20others%2C%20largely%20made%20of%20scrap%20leather.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20their%20brand%20is%20sustainability%2C%20functionality%20and%20durability.%20As%20their%20website%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CBy%20making%20the%20best%20use%20of%20discarded%20leather%2C%20fabrics%20and%20threads%2C%20we%20eliminate%20the%20initiation%20of%20raw%20material%20processing%2C%20resulting%20in%20upcycling%20the%20existing%20material%20towards%20a%20functional%20cause.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Guneet-Monga-1695910108.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Check%20out%20this%20luxury%20fashion%20brand%20making%20products%20out%20of%20waste%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Guneet-Monga-1695910108.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Guneet-Monga-1695910108-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FEconock-Guneet-Monga-1695910108-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebet